Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.65,0:03:17.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to touch them and some don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.52,0:03:27.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi sweetheart.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.12,0:03:28.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.12,0:03:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,God bless you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.40,0:03:31.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at this person's head.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.40,0:03:35.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it something else?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.31,0:03:36.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.31,0:03:37.31,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll see you tomorrow morning?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.31,0:03:38.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.31,0:03:39.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you ever eat there?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.31,0:03:40.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.44,0:03:41.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.44,0:03:43.69,Default,,0,0,0,,That's nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.69,0:03:46.03,Default,,0,0,0,,That's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.03,0:03:47.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, look who's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.03,0:03:48.03,Default,,0,0,0,,elo.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.03,0:03:50.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, the ladies and the gentlemen.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.77,0:03:51.77,Default,,0,0,0,,There's the gentleman here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.77,0:03:52.77,Default,,0,0,0,,The ladies.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.77,0:03:53.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You get a second one.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.77,0:03:55.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You get a second one, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.69,0:03:56.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, look here, who's John, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.69,0:03:57.69,Default,,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.69,0:03:58.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Gloria in excelsis Deo.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.69,0:03:59.69,Default,,0,0,0,,To Thee, O Lord, do we surrender our lives to Thee and give No remarkable sacrifice
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.69,0:04:01.30,Default,,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.30,0:04:02.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It's before we die that He comes and sits down before us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.30,0:04:03.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Until we die, Lord, have mercy on us and forgive us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.30,0:04:04.30,Default,,0,0,0,,In Jesus' name, amen.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.30,0:04:05.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Amen.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.30,0:04:06.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Amen.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.30,0:04:07.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Amen.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.30,0:04:08.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Amen.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.30,0:04:09.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Amen.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.37,0:04:10.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Amen.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.37,0:04:12.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Amen.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.37,0:04:13.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Amen.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.37,0:04:14.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Amen.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.37,0:04:36.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Amen.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.49,0:04:37.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Amen.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.49,0:04:42.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Amen.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.19,0:04:43.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Amen.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.23,0:04:44.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Amen.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.23,0:04:45.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Amen.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.23,0:04:46.76,Default,,0,0,0,,this day, and evermore.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.62,0:04:51.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Anybody disagree?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.69,0:04:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that noise I heard?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.64,0:04:58.05,Default,,0,0,0,,A sucking sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.31,0:05:03.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.86,0:05:05.86,Default,,0,0,0,,So we can sit down.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.95,0:05:09.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me, how many new people are there here today?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.57,0:05:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,New?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.18,0:05:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.30,0:05:13.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Not many.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.29,0:05:14.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.94,0:05:17.56,Default,,0,0,0,,We may reverse the way we usually do it in that case.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.54,0:05:20.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Those brights are very bright in my eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.24,0:05:21.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't see a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.68,0:05:22.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Are they supposed to be that bright?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.29,0:05:25.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Help.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.06,0:05:26.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Help.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.49,0:05:27.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Are they supposed to be that bright?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.13,0:05:29.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Help.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.68,0:05:29.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Help.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.95,0:05:30.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Help.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.18,0:05:30.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Help.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.62,0:05:30.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.50,0:05:32.07,Default,,0,0,0,,They are?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.83,0:05:34.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.20,0:05:36.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't see anything anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.45,0:05:39.36,Default,,0,0,0,,What's there to see?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.51,0:05:42.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just everybody you love, that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.13,0:05:47.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, there's not many new people.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.04,0:05:52.41,Default,,0,0,0,,So generally, we start from scratch.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.41,0:05:54.52,Default,,0,0,0,,We start with the scale.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.85,0:06:00.17,Default,,0,0,0,,And just briefly sketch how it all came about for people that are new.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.17,0:06:02.67,Default,,0,0,0,,But for those who have been here many times, they've heard it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.45,0:06:07.45,Default,,0,0,0,,So I thought we'll start with where we usually end up, which is the subject of today.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.83,0:06:17.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it was because some people like to see the lectures on videotape,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.24,0:06:18.66,Default,,0,0,0,,and therefore we start from the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.13,0:06:22.24,Default,,0,0,0,,But they'll have to get an earlier one.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.92,0:06:23.16,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.19,0:06:24.07,Default,,0,0,0,,So we're going to start.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.32,0:06:26.31,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going to start.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.31,0:06:29.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't cue you into what I was going to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.01,0:06:31.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to start with the last three.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.18,0:06:34.77,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going to start with the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.12,0:06:38.75,Default,,0,0,0,,The last three, which I can't read.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.97,0:06:39.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, well, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.20,0:06:45.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.22,0:06:58.16,Default,,0,0,0,,So we're going to start with, hmm, here it is on the list here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.39,0:06:58.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.25,0:07:07.41,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going to start with 97.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.37,0:07:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll do 97, 98, and 99.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.25,0:07:12.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.56,0:07:12.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.70,0:07:16.06,Default,,0,0,0,,So we've done almost 100 slides.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.76,0:07:18.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa, boy, oh, boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.74,0:07:22.10,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.97,0:07:25.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Today's lecture is on the miraculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.80,0:07:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The miraculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.22,0:07:36.11,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's a very interesting subject, and I wish I'd had more time to spend on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.17,0:07:37.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to spend more time in the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.37,0:07:43.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Because today's world, we don't think of the miraculous as a reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.06,0:07:47.42,Default,,0,0,0,,We think of it as something that happened centuries ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.98,0:07:49.48,Default,,0,0,0,,and it was so...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.68,0:07:54.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Incredibly unusual that it changed the course of history.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.35,0:08:00.27,Default,,0,0,0,,And so people don't think of the miraculous in terms of everyday life, their own life,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.10,0:08:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,and that of others, unless you're doing a course of miracles,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.16,0:08:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,,in which case you are thinking about it, and asking for a miracle all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.05,0:08:13.26,Default,,0,0,0,,The first miracle is that you're asking for a miracle.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.26,0:08:14.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You already got one.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.13,0:08:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,So the miraculous is usually held in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.00,0:08:23.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.24,0:08:25.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Mind is somewhere in the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.18,0:08:30.37,Default,,0,0,0,,And, of course, when it did occur in the past, it did change human history.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.87,0:08:37.62,Default,,0,0,0,,The great miracles of the past totally changed the history of the world,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.79,0:08:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,especially the history of the Western world.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.47,0:08:43.87,Default,,0,0,0,,And so, therefore, we'll review just how that came about.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.45,0:08:49.33,Default,,0,0,0,,We found out that people under 200 do not experience the miraculous,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.16,0:08:52.66,Default,,0,0,0,,do not witness it, and do not experience it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.87,0:08:56.41,Default,,0,0,0,,And you notice all the skeptics.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.44,0:09:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,The skeptics who calibrate below 200 poo-poo the miraculous, of course,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.80,0:09:04.11,Default,,0,0,0,,because they've never witnessed it and never experienced it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.19,0:09:05.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It is not a reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.62,0:09:08.71,Default,,0,0,0,,So it sounds like a dreamer's fantasy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.26,0:09:13.52,Default,,0,0,0,,The miraculous, as we'll find out, is relatively commonplace.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.14,0:09:19.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Almost everybody in this room has already experienced the miraculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.12,0:09:20.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Resist.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.92,0:09:22.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Almost everybody in this room.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.42,0:09:23.73,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact, everybody in this room has.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.79,0:09:25.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.32,0:09:28.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't want one of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.48,0:09:29.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't want one of them to sneak in the audience.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.77,0:09:34.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.08,0:09:38.65,Default,,0,0,0,,We're safe from the unholy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.01,0:09:41.15,Default,,0,0,0,,The ungodly.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.10,0:09:47.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, therefore, it has something to do with karmic merit.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.65,0:09:55.27,Default,,0,0,0,,And people say, well, yes, but what about people who are deep in the pits of hell and horror and negativity
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.27,0:09:59.70,Default,,0,0,0,,and experienced a transformative miracle?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.20,0:10:02.26,Default,,0,0,0,,They didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.28,0:10:05.35,Default,,0,0,0,,They didn't experience the miracle when they were below 200.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.12,0:10:08.37,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened is they were way below 200.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.75,0:10:13.95,Default,,0,0,0,,And in despair, they prayed fervently to God.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.11,0:10:15.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, God, please help me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.22,0:10:18.05,Default,,0,0,0,,They instantly jumped above 200.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.37,0:10:21.58,Default,,0,0,0,,And therefore, they were over 200 when they experienced the miraculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.27,0:10:28.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I had to clear that up about Emperor Constantine, which we'll get to,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.11,0:10:33.21,Default,,0,0,0,,who, of course, the miracle that he experienced in the year 320.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.40,0:10:38.71,Default,,0,0,0,,And then in 312, changed all of human history forever, quite a.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.71,0:10:42.75,Default,,0,0,0,,So the miraculous then can have a stunning impact.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.64,0:10:54.02,Default,,0,0,0,,So we'll put that back on, and I'll start with, I just wanted us to be aware that the miraculous is commonplace,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.76,0:10:58.25,Default,,0,0,0,,but unobserved and not recognized.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.28,0:11:04.47,Default,,0,0,0,,We always talk in these lectures about,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.16,0:11:10.07,Default,,0,0,0,,transcend the level of the intellect, which sees everything in terms of causality,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.28,0:11:11.62,Default,,0,0,0,,of this causing of that,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.98,0:11:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,with a time dimension and the energies of force.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.78,0:11:25.23,Default,,0,0,0,,The other downside of that is that gives you the same picture of God.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.37,0:11:27.97,Default,,0,0,0,,God started someplace and is going to end someplace.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.02,0:11:31.45,Default,,0,0,0,,And God is experiencing time, et cetera.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.92,0:11:37.66,Default,,0,0,0,,The miraculous occurs outside of time, and it is not a consequence of causality.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.99,0:11:40.78,Default,,0,0,0,,There isn't a this causing of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.55,0:11:49.98,Default,,0,0,0,,All things, all things happen, all phenomena occur as a consequence
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.98,0:11:55.86,Default,,0,0,0,,of potentiality becoming actuality, and the process is one of emergence.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.86,0:12:01.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Because you picture things, you witness them sequentially,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.62,0:12:05.33,Default,,0,0,0,,you think that sequence is out in the universe.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.59,0:12:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no sequence in the universe.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.28,0:12:10.59,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no sequence in the universe.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.61,0:12:13.71,Default,,0,0,0,,The sequence is in the observer.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.80,0:12:17.71,Default,,0,0,0,,The phenomena are not occurring sequentially.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.14,0:12:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The witnessing is occurring sequentially.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.90,0:12:26.33,Default,,0,0,0,,As the thing emerges like this, you do a stop, stop, stop, stop, stop, stop,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.47,0:12:31.48,Default,,0,0,0,,and you think those are all stages, but it's actually all just one action.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.12,0:12:33.36,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.25,0:12:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Because everything emerges from potentiality into actuality,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.70,0:12:43.34,Default,,0,0,0,,it does so.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.84,0:12:45.46,Default,,0,0,0,,And the conditions are appropriate.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.00,0:12:53.82,Default,,0,0,0,,So, the seed does not, the seed does not become a seedling in the middle of Winter.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.82,0:12:58.70,Default,,0,0,0,,So, because the local conditions, however its potential lays there all Winter long,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.49,0:13:05.23,Default,,0,0,0,,the potential of some, what do they call them, century plants
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.23,0:13:10.07,Default,,0,0,0,,may lay underground for a hundred years and then suddenly the right conditions, it emerges.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.07,0:13:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,So, the potentiality is, is within.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.40,0:13:15.29,Default,,0,0,0,,And it waits.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.29,0:13:21.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Rates to be actualized in local conditions are favorable.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.36,0:13:25.41,Default,,0,0,0,,One of the local conditions that is very, very powerful
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.41,0:13:30.05,Default,,0,0,0,,because of the Heisenberg Principle is prayer and supplication.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.46,0:13:35.03,Default,,0,0,0,,In this particular lifetime, from the lowest pits of hell
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.03,0:13:39.65,Default,,0,0,0,,to suddenly the infinite presence,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.86,0:13:46.32,Default,,0,0,0,,all came about as a consequence of a profound supplication.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.32,0:13:50.72,Default,,0,0,0,,If there is a God, I ask him to help me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.14,0:13:54.24,Default,,0,0,0,,And then, a 180.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.19,0:13:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,From the endless pits of endless suffering and agony,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.49,0:14:00.62,Default,,0,0,0,,foreverness of hell,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.57,0:14:06.47,Default,,0,0,0,,suddenly the dazzling brilliance of the source of existence itself
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.47,0:14:11.73,Default,,0,0,0,,shone forth, the ice, transformed everything to this day.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.20,0:14:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,So, the miraculous is not the result of causation.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.47,0:14:26.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore, there's no person causing a miracle.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.85,0:14:30.49,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no person that does miracles.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.24,0:14:34.98,Default,,0,0,0,,People advertise that they're miracle workers.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.80,0:14:38.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You should always count, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.28,0:14:44.41,Default,,0,0,0,,The miraculous we've observed all around the world,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.53,0:14:45.96,Default,,0,0,0,,myself, many a time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.11,0:14:53.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It's always a phenomena that you don't even get until it's happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.39,0:14:54.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You witness it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.67,0:14:58.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Because of a certain energy,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.74,0:15:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,and because of the supplication on the part of the person,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.75,0:15:05.87,Default,,0,0,0,,and because of karmic appropriateness,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.50,0:15:10.37,Default,,0,0,0,,the phenomena that would seem scientifically unlikely happen,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.94,0:15:12.87,Default,,0,0,0,,and they happen relatively often.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.87,0:15:17.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Not infrequent, but relatively frequent.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.92,0:15:23.40,Default,,0,0,0,,So, the mechanics of it is that the potentiality is there.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.01,0:15:27.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Karmic propensity is one of the local conditions.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.13,0:15:29.91,Default,,0,0,0,,The prevailing energy field,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.08,0:15:31.62,Default,,0,0,0,,which is one of the local conditions.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.62,0:15:38.62,Default,,0,0,0,,And praying, of course, increases the power of the context,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.62,0:15:41.32,Default,,0,0,0,,which is the spiritual energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.32,0:15:44.82,Default,,0,0,0,,So, in the presence of a high spiritual energy,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.82,0:15:49.03,Default,,0,0,0,,a likelihood becomes an actuality.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.03,0:15:52.79,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like the apple is waiting to fall from the tree.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.79,0:15:57.36,Default,,0,0,0,,And when a certain energy walks by the tree, it drops.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.36,0:16:01.77,Default,,0,0,0,,But that which walked by the tree doesn't cause the apple.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.77,0:16:02.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.77,0:16:08.77,Default,,0,0,0,,It just precipitates a potentiality by virtue of the power of the energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.77,0:16:16.96,Default,,0,0,0,,From the viewpoint of linear causality, it's, of course, not explicable.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.96,0:16:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,And therefore, even all the most famous miracles of history
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.96,0:16:26.96,Default,,0,0,0,,are pooh-poohed by a certain percentage of the population routinely.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.96,0:16:32.21,Default,,0,0,0,,The difficulty is, it's because the cynic and the skeptic, etc.,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.21,0:16:33.73,Default,,0,0,0,,does not understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.73,0:16:39.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It does not understand context and doesn't understand the non-linear.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.04,0:16:45.04,Default,,0,0,0,,The pedestrian mind is only concerned with the linear, provable, factual, material,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.04,0:16:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,and thinks in terms of a limited causality.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.04,0:16:51.34,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't understand context.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.34,0:16:55.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Because the one statement in this context is true,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.34,0:16:57.34,Default,,0,0,0,,in this context it's false.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.34,0:17:00.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore, context is profoundly important,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.34,0:17:03.34,Default,,0,0,0,,and you ignore it at your own peril.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.33,0:17:08.66,Default,,0,0,0,,The unexpected occurrence from the viewpoint of linear causality.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.66,0:17:10.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, the mind believes that,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.72,0:17:12.72,Default,,0,0,0,,and because it believes that,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.72,0:17:17.72,Default,,0,0,0,,it misses about 99% of the miraculous that's occurring around them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.72,0:17:18.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.78,0:17:22.78,Default,,0,0,0,,The average mind misses about 99% resist.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.78,0:17:24.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Misses 100% resist.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.78,0:17:27.78,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it misses 99%.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.78,0:17:31.17,Default,,0,0,0,,The miraculous is happening all around you,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.17,0:17:33.17,Default,,0,0,0,,and you're not even noticing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.17,0:17:34.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.17,0:17:36.17,Default,,0,0,0,,And you're busy saying you don't believe in miracles,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.17,0:17:39.17,Default,,0,0,0,,and they're all happening all around you in one thing or another.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.48,0:17:45.64,Default,,0,0,0,,So it isn't that they're rare.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.64,0:17:49.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It's that people are not conscious of them
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.64,0:17:54.64,Default,,0,0,0,,as a present reality or potential reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.64,0:17:57.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Seeing rarity due to limitation of the observer.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.64,0:17:59.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It isn't that miracles are rare.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.64,0:18:03.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It's that people who are capable of witnessing them are rare.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.64,0:18:07.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Even when it's right in front of their eye,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.64,0:18:09.64,Default,,0,0,0,,they can't see it, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.64,0:18:11.64,Default,,0,0,0,,And I used to watch that sometimes,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.64,0:18:13.64,Default,,0,0,0,,and it was just delirious.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.64,0:18:19.05,Default,,0,0,0,,And, in fact, a lot of people will go temporarily unconscious.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.05,0:18:21.05,Default,,0,0,0,,And there was a period of my time
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.05,0:18:26.05,Default,,0,0,0,,when the miraculous was continuous and rather dazzling.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.05,0:18:30.05,Default,,0,0,0,,And I would watch a person witnessing it,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.05,0:18:34.59,Default,,0,0,0,,and they would actually go unconscious for a split second,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.59,0:18:36.59,Default,,0,0,0,,and not see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.59,0:18:38.59,Default,,0,0,0,,They actually couldn't see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.59,0:18:40.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It was really strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.73,0:18:43.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.63,0:18:50.75,Default,,0,0,0,,So if you believe that miracles are rare or not possible
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.75,0:18:54.75,Default,,0,0,0,,and only happen in the presence of angels and great saints,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.75,0:18:56.75,Default,,0,0,0,,you probably won't witness any.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.75,0:18:59.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You won't be aware that you're witnessing them.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.75,0:19:01.79,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.79,0:19:06.30,Default,,0,0,0,,They are also facilitated by favorable karmic propensity,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.30,0:19:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,as is the witnessing of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.40,0:19:13.55,Default,,0,0,0,,The apple doesn't fall from the tree
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.55,0:19:16.55,Default,,0,0,0,,until it's reached a certain state of ripeness.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.55,0:19:19.72,Default,,0,0,0,,So the whole purpose of spiritual evolution
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.72,0:19:22.72,Default,,0,0,0,,is to transcend from the Lord
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.72,0:19:24.72,Default,,0,0,0,,to the higher levels of consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.72,0:19:28.72,Default,,0,0,0,,And as you do, the miraculous becomes more and more frequent.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.72,0:19:32.84,Default,,0,0,0,,And I don't even see the miraculous anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.84,0:19:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I stopped seeing them years ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.46,0:19:38.31,Default,,0,0,0,,because they weren't the miraculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.31,0:19:40.31,Default,,0,0,0,,They were just everyday.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.31,0:19:46.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the way the world is.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.83,0:19:48.83,Default,,0,0,0,,The way the world is,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.83,0:19:52.83,Default,,0,0,0,,is once you see emergence of potentiality into actuality,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.83,0:19:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,once you see that everything is happening autonomously of its own,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.50,0:20:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,then you no longer differentiate the miraculous from the non-miraculous,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.50,0:20:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,because for this hand to move up in the air
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.50,0:20:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,and try to express something non-verbally
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.50,0:20:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,is already outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.50,0:20:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, it's happening on and so on.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.50,0:20:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't ask it to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.50,0:20:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't write it up ahead of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.50,0:20:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, in so and so time,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.50,0:20:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I will have the right hand go to this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.50,0:20:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The fingers will go up.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.50,0:20:25.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, it all happens autonomously and spontaneously.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.64,0:20:28.64,Default,,0,0,0,,So you might say all of life,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.64,0:20:31.64,Default,,0,0,0,,in all of its aspects,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.64,0:20:36.64,Default,,0,0,0,,is, on one level of reality, the miraculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.64,0:20:40.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Human existence itself, you might say.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.98,0:20:42.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, the greatest miracles
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.98,0:20:44.98,Default,,0,0,0,,of all time,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.98,0:20:49.17,Default,,0,0,0,,then we'll get into historical miracles.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.17,0:20:52.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Because the average person can't witness,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.26,0:20:55.26,Default,,0,0,0,,doesn't observe that which is extraordinary,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.26,0:21:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,because it's not within their realm of reality,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.56,0:21:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,they only observe when they become very, very pronounced.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.96,0:21:09.40,Default,,0,0,0,,And for the audience,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.40,0:21:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,for the participants then,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.40,0:21:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Jesus' 33 miracles,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.40,0:21:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,,which we've asked before,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.40,0:21:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll ask him again,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.40,0:21:20.40,Default,,0,0,0,,make sure he didn't change his mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.40,0:21:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,,In the meantime,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.40,0:21:23.97,Default,,0,0,0,,we have permission to ask this.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.97,0:21:28.13,Default,,0,0,0,,The 33 documented miracles of Jesus
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.13,0:21:36.74,Default,,0,0,0,,were indeed miraculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.74,0:21:38.90,Default,,0,0,0,,So they did indeed exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.90,0:21:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,And why were they so dramatic?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.08,0:21:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Because otherwise people wouldn't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.22,0:21:46.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Unless you do something,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.22,0:21:49.22,Default,,0,0,0,,unless something occurs dramatically,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.22,0:21:51.75,Default,,0,0,0,,the witness doesn't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.75,0:21:53.75,Default,,0,0,0,,The fact that the bust that would have killed you
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.75,0:21:56.75,Default,,0,0,0,,just veered off one split second before
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.75,0:21:59.75,Default,,0,0,0,,doesn't seem, you know, it seems lucky.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.75,0:22:02.75,Default,,0,0,0,,So the average mind dismisses the miraculous
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.75,0:22:04.75,Default,,0,0,0,,as lucky, fortuitous,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.75,0:22:08.24,Default,,0,0,0,,and doesn't see that it is the operation
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.24,0:22:11.24,Default,,0,0,0,,of the potentiality becoming actual
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.24,0:22:13.24,Default,,0,0,0,,when appropriate conditions, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.24,0:22:16.63,Default,,0,0,0,,The 33 miracles then are, of course,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.63,0:22:20.03,Default,,0,0,0,,the average person is, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.03,0:22:22.03,Default,,0,0,0,,unaware of enlightened or advanced states.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.03,0:22:24.24,Default,,0,0,0,,And in today's world,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.24,0:22:26.24,Default,,0,0,0,,that's extremely so.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.24,0:22:30.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It was so in the days of Jesus as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.26,0:22:32.46,Default,,0,0,0,,And therefore,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.46,0:22:37.54,Default,,0,0,0,,the presence of divinity within a teacher
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.54,0:22:39.54,Default,,0,0,0,,was not recognized
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.54,0:22:43.54,Default,,0,0,0,,until they did something theatrical.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.54,0:22:45.19,Default,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.19,0:22:48.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You can be enlightened and be speaking great truths
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.19,0:22:50.19,Default,,0,0,0,,that will change mankind.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.19,0:22:54.53,Default,,0,0,0,,But it isn't until you turn water into wine
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.53,0:22:55.53,Default,,0,0,0,,that people say,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.53,0:22:56.53,Default,,0,0,0,,oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.84,0:23:08.84,Default,,0,0,0,,So the 33 miracles were, of course,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.84,0:23:15.13,Default,,0,0,0,,dramatic and called attention to his divinity.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.13,0:23:18.25,Default,,0,0,0,,And therefore, he became famous
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.25,0:23:23.38,Default,,0,0,0,,because the average unsophisticated mind
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.38,0:23:26.59,Default,,0,0,0,,doesn't understand what the presence of God
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.59,0:23:27.59,Default,,0,0,0,,within a teacher means.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.59,0:23:29.59,Default,,0,0,0,,And so they wait for something special,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.59,0:23:32.15,Default,,0,0,0,,something spectacular.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.15,0:23:34.15,Default,,0,0,0,,When something spectacular occurs,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.15,0:23:36.15,Default,,0,0,0,,then they are convinced.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.15,0:23:39.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Either that or they get spooked out.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.40,0:23:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,They get spooked.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.00,0:23:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.00,0:23:51.17,Default,,0,0,0,,So we won't have these flowers turn into birds
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.17,0:23:53.17,Default,,0,0,0,,and fly away this morning
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.17,0:23:55.17,Default,,0,0,0,,because people might think that we
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.17,0:23:57.17,Default,,0,0,0,,have something up our sleeve.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.17,0:24:00.39,Default,,0,0,0,,There's, you know, the debunkers.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.39,0:24:01.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I love debunkers.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.39,0:24:02.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You see them on TV
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.39,0:24:04.39,Default,,0,0,0,,and they can think up the most incredible
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.39,0:24:07.39,Default,,0,0,0,,engineering, mechanical explanations
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.39,0:24:09.39,Default,,0,0,0,,for anything that would happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.39,0:24:12.39,Default,,0,0,0,,So it doesn't do any good for these to turn into birds
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.39,0:24:14.39,Default,,0,0,0,,because the debunker will get on a TV program
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.39,0:24:16.39,Default,,0,0,0,,within a month or two
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.39,0:24:18.39,Default,,0,0,0,,and show you how he can manipulate these lights
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.39,0:24:20.39,Default,,0,0,0,,and make these look like birds.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.39,0:24:27.39,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you know, the need to deny the non-linear,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.39,0:24:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,it's so interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.96,0:24:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,In our own time and, of course, throughout history,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.96,0:24:41.72,Default,,0,0,0,,the stigmata have been a subject of discussion and query
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.72,0:24:45.72,Default,,0,0,0,,and the Vatican catalogs them
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.72,0:24:48.78,Default,,0,0,0,,and they go through quite a whole thing
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.78,0:24:50.92,Default,,0,0,0,,to make sure it's a stigmata.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.92,0:24:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Stigmata that were recently endorsed by the,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.92,0:24:59.92,Default,,0,0,0,,let's do the stigmata that were recently endorsed by the Vatican,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.92,0:25:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,they were indeed stigmata.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.92,0:25:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, the church is extremely careful
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.92,0:25:09.43,Default,,0,0,0,,and goes through a great deal of effort
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.43,0:25:12.94,Default,,0,0,0,,to document the stigmata.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.94,0:25:14.94,Default,,0,0,0,,So how does stigmata come about?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.94,0:25:18.94,Default,,0,0,0,,They come about by virtue of intense adoration
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.94,0:25:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,and identification.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.16,0:25:26.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Intense identification and adoration of Jesus Christ
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.79,0:25:30.11,Default,,0,0,0,,can bring bleeding nail marks in your hand
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.11,0:25:32.11,Default,,0,0,0,,and they do indeed bleed.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.11,0:25:35.27,Default,,0,0,0,,They're indeed there.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.27,0:25:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,,They're not artificial
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.20,0:25:42.65,Default,,0,0,0,,because the identification is so powerful and strong
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.65,0:25:46.75,Default,,0,0,0,,and psychosomatic conditions appropriate
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.75,0:25:48.75,Default,,0,0,0,,and with karmic principle,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.75,0:25:52.75,Default,,0,0,0,,with certain karmic entitlement.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.75,0:25:55.75,Default,,0,0,0,,These stigmata actually,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.75,0:26:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,the stigmata are very often used as a sign of sainthood
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.00,0:26:04.09,Default,,0,0,0,,and the stigmata tend to occur
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.09,0:26:07.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I would think from about 570 and up.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.09,0:26:09.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to get up here.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.09,0:26:13.09,Default,,0,0,0,,The stigmata occur from 570 and up,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.09,0:26:16.09,Default,,0,0,0,,which is the level of sainthood.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.09,0:26:18.09,Default,,0,0,0,,So the Catholic Church is right.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.10,0:26:25.03,Default,,0,0,0,,They're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.03,0:26:30.03,Default,,0,0,0,,The stigmata occur at about that level of consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.03,0:26:33.03,Default,,0,0,0,,which is exactly the same level as sainthood
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.03,0:26:36.28,Default,,0,0,0,,and therefore consciousness calibration
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.28,0:26:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,,we document
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.28,0:26:39.28,Default,,0,0,0,,that it is actual, truthful,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.28,0:26:42.48,Default,,0,0,0,,and the Church is correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.48,0:26:46.38,Default,,0,0,0,,This canonized, the saints,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.38,0:26:50.73,Default,,0,0,0,,these were canonized in 2006
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.73,0:26:56.73,Default,,0,0,0,,and those that were canonized by the Pope in 2006
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.73,0:27:00.59,Default,,0,0,0,,were indeed saints, resist.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.59,0:27:03.59,Default,,0,0,0,,So you just want to document that there is,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.59,0:27:05.59,Default,,0,0,0,,sainthood is a reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.59,0:27:08.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Stigmata are sometimes a consequence
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.59,0:27:11.59,Default,,0,0,0,,of that expression of that reality
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.59,0:27:15.78,Default,,0,0,0,,that you can validate it scientifically
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.78,0:27:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,and the great terror that the Vatican puts in
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.88,0:27:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,to canonizing saints
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.88,0:27:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,is because they do not want to take any chance
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.92,0:27:27.92,Default,,0,0,0,,of error.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.92,0:27:30.07,Default,,0,0,0,,How do these things come about?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.07,0:27:34.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, Jung had an interesting concept
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.65,0:27:38.39,Default,,0,0,0,,called synesthesia.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.39,0:27:44.57,Default,,0,0,0,,That phenomena will tend to pull together
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.57,0:27:47.83,Default,,0,0,0,,into what I would call an energy field
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.83,0:27:49.83,Default,,0,0,0,,that is not accidental.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.83,0:27:54.11,Default,,0,0,0,,That is, it's the composite of all that has been
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.11,0:27:57.59,Default,,0,0,0,,added to it over the centuries.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.59,0:28:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Synesthesia has to do with time and location.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.32,0:28:06.32,Default,,0,0,0,,People think that it's lucky
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.32,0:28:09.32,Default,,0,0,0,,that they were all just there at that time.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.32,0:28:11.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.32,0:28:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,There was a sailboat and there was two people on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.00,0:28:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,And when it drowned,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.00,0:28:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,but there was this sailboat there
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.00,0:28:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,and I got saved.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.00,0:28:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,So while the sailboat had the whole sea to be on,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.00,0:28:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,why was it within a couple hundred feet
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.00,0:28:28.51,Default,,0,0,0,,of a drowning sailor?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.51,0:28:30.51,Default,,0,0,0,,So that has to do with,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.51,0:28:33.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Jung would call it synchronicity,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.51,0:28:35.51,Default,,0,0,0,,synesthesia, synchronicity,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.51,0:28:37.51,Default,,0,0,0,,that those things are not by accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.51,0:28:40.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, we've been students of energy fields
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.51,0:28:43.83,Default,,0,0,0,,and we see that an energy field
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.83,0:28:46.83,Default,,0,0,0,,then tends to dominate the phenomena
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.83,0:28:51.58,Default,,0,0,0,,within that energy field.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.58,0:28:53.65,Default,,0,0,0,,One of the most,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.65,0:28:56.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Jesus Christ changed all of history
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.65,0:29:00.88,Default,,0,0,0,,and the miracles helped establish
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.88,0:29:03.74,Default,,0,0,0,,who he really was.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.74,0:29:08.27,Default,,0,0,0,,So his miracles changed the course of history, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.27,0:29:12.81,Default,,0,0,0,,That was 2006 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.81,0:29:16.10,Default,,0,0,0,,2006 AD.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.03,0:29:24.85,Default,,0,0,0,,AD, AD, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.85,0:29:27.85,Default,,0,0,0,,2006 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.85,0:29:31.15,Default,,0,0,0,,In the year 312,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.15,0:29:33.15,Default,,0,0,0,,now the history of the Roman Empire
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.15,0:29:34.15,Default,,0,0,0,,is extremely interesting
Dialogue: 0,0:29:34.15,0:29:36.15,Default,,0,0,0,,and its correlation with religious history
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.15,0:29:38.47,Default,,0,0,0,,is extremely interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.47,0:29:40.95,Default,,0,0,0,,The Emperor Constantine,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.95,0:29:42.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I forget what year he was born,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.95,0:29:45.26,Default,,0,0,0,,but anyway,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.26,0:29:47.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Constantine was an emperor
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.26,0:29:50.72,Default,,0,0,0,,and Constantine for some reason
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.72,0:29:54.20,Default,,0,0,0,,sought direction from God.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.20,0:29:57.20,Default,,0,0,0,,He was facing a great enemy,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.20,0:29:58.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I think his brother-in-law,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:58.20,0:30:00.20,Default,,0,0,0,,with a great army
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.20,0:30:02.54,Default,,0,0,0,,for the control of Rome.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.54,0:30:09.33,Default,,0,0,0,,And Constantine calibrated at 195
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.33,0:30:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,in those days.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.00,0:30:14.20,Default,,0,0,0,,When confronted with,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.20,0:30:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,dealing with this issue,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:16.20,0:30:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Constantine suddenly went into a state of devotion
Dialogue: 0,0:30:20.20,0:30:23.83,Default,,0,0,0,,and he prayed to God for a sign.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.83,0:30:28.55,Default,,0,0,0,,He was at 195.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.55,0:30:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,,But then when he prayed to God
Dialogue: 0,0:30:32.48,0:30:35.53,Default,,0,0,0,,for a sign,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.53,0:30:38.53,Default,,0,0,0,,he entreated God with great sincerity.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.53,0:30:42.85,Default,,0,0,0,,He automatically jumped to 245.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.85,0:30:46.36,Default,,0,0,0,,So it wasn't his prior state.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.36,0:30:48.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It was his new state
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.36,0:30:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,that summoned forth a sign.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.10,0:30:54.10,Default,,0,0,0,,So Constantine,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.10,0:30:56.65,Default,,0,0,0,,when he looked up in the sky,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.65,0:30:59.65,Default,,0,0,0,,he saw a light in the form of a cross
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.65,0:31:00.65,Default,,0,0,0,,and it was a sign from God.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.65,0:31:03.68,Default,,0,0,0,,So he put together,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:03.68,0:31:05.96,Default,,0,0,0,,the two Greeks,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:05.96,0:31:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,he put together the letters
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.96,0:31:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,chi and rho,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.96,0:31:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,which became the symbol
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.96,0:31:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,which was put on the shields
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.96,0:31:16.27,Default,,0,0,0,,of his soldiers.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.27,0:31:18.38,Default,,0,0,0,,And the message was
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.38,0:31:21.38,Default,,0,0,0,,that this would give him great power.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.38,0:31:24.64,Default,,0,0,0,,And Constantine then defeated
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.64,0:31:27.30,Default,,0,0,0,,his brother-in-law
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.30,0:31:30.36,Default,,0,0,0,,and became the great emperor
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.36,0:31:33.26,Default,,0,0,0,,of all time.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.26,0:31:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,So Constantine
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.88,0:31:45.88,Default,,0,0,0,,declared Christianity
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.88,0:31:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,to be the official church
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.88,0:31:50.26,Default,,0,0,0,,of the Roman Empire.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.26,0:31:51.26,Default,,0,0,0,,At the same time,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:51.26,0:31:54.29,Default,,0,0,0,,he was tolerant of non-Christian churches
Dialogue: 0,0:31:54.29,0:31:56.29,Default,,0,0,0,,and did not banish them or anything,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:56.29,0:31:59.35,Default,,0,0,0,,but he established Christianity.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:59.35,0:32:00.35,Default,,0,0,0,,And of course,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.35,0:32:01.35,Default,,0,0,0,,the Roman Empire
Dialogue: 0,0:32:01.35,0:32:03.35,Default,,0,0,0,,is what became Western civilization.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.35,0:32:05.43,Default,,0,0,0,,All of Europe,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.43,0:32:06.43,Default,,0,0,0,,all of Europe,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.43,0:32:07.43,Default,,0,0,0,,America,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.43,0:32:10.43,Default,,0,0,0,,the entire Western world
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.43,0:32:15.06,Default,,0,0,0,,emerged out of that decision of Constantine.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.06,0:32:17.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Quite a powerful miracle.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.80,0:32:25.80,Default,,0,0,0,,And Constantine did indeed
Dialogue: 0,0:32:25.80,0:32:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,see a miraculous sign from God
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.88,0:32:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,in the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:30.88,0:32:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,He did indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:34.96,0:32:40.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, the debunkers hate miracles,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.60,0:32:43.86,Default,,0,0,0,,so if you look up Constantine
Dialogue: 0,0:32:43.86,0:32:44.86,Default,,0,0,0,,on the internet,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.86,0:32:46.86,Default,,0,0,0,,whatever you call that machine,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:46.86,0:32:48.90,Default,,0,0,0,,the system they have there,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:49.90,0:32:52.02,Default,,0,0,0,,a debunker will get in there and say,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.02,0:32:54.02,Default,,0,0,0,,well, he claimed that.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.02,0:32:55.16,Default,,0,0,0,,However,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.16,0:32:57.16,Default,,0,0,0,,skeptics affirm that
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.16,0:32:59.16,Default,,0,0,0,,then they named three planets
Dialogue: 0,0:32:59.16,0:33:00.16,Default,,0,0,0,,were in such an alignment
Dialogue: 0,0:33:00.16,0:33:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,,that that's really what he saw,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:02.16,0:33:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,except it was daylights.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.16,0:33:07.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't see planets in daylights.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.16,0:33:09.16,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.16,0:33:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,it's just amazing
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.16,0:33:11.16,Default,,0,0,0,,how the mind stretches
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.16,0:33:13.16,Default,,0,0,0,,to try and cancel any recognition
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.16,0:33:15.16,Default,,0,0,0,,of the reality of divinity
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.16,0:33:19.16,Default,,0,0,0,,or non-linear reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.16,0:33:20.16,Default,,0,0,0,,These three planets,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.16,0:33:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,he saw the three planets,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:21.16,0:33:22.16,Default,,0,0,0,,and that's what he saw.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:22.16,0:33:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It wasn't a miracle at all,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.16,0:33:26.53,Default,,0,0,0,,except they forget it was daytime
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.53,0:33:27.53,Default,,0,0,0,,when he saw them.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:27.53,0:33:28.53,Default,,0,0,0,,So,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.53,0:33:29.82,Default,,0,0,0,,anyway,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.82,0:33:31.82,Default,,0,0,0,,they did put that insignia
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.82,0:33:32.82,Default,,0,0,0,,on the Roman shield.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.82,0:33:33.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a very famous one
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.82,0:33:35.82,Default,,0,0,0,,with a loop around.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.82,0:33:36.82,Default,,0,0,0,,And the Roman legions
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.82,0:33:38.82,Default,,0,0,0,,were indeed formidable.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.82,0:33:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,,The Roman legions were indeed
Dialogue: 0,0:33:40.82,0:33:42.82,Default,,0,0,0,,formidable, formidable,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.82,0:33:46.85,Default,,0,0,0,,the most powerful country in the world then,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.85,0:33:49.85,Default,,0,0,0,,which has come down to the present time.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.85,0:33:52.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It's America.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.36,0:33:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,And America is a consequence then
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.36,0:33:58.36,Default,,0,0,0,,of the Judeo-Christian legacy
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.36,0:34:00.36,Default,,0,0,0,,and really the decision of Constantine
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.36,0:34:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,in the year 312.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.80,0:34:09.23,Default,,0,0,0,,The other miracles are,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:09.23,0:34:10.23,Default,,0,0,0,,as I say,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.23,0:34:12.23,Default,,0,0,0,,they're not recognized
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.23,0:34:14.23,Default,,0,0,0,,and they don't seem to occur
Dialogue: 0,0:34:14.23,0:34:15.23,Default,,0,0,0,,until you become aware
Dialogue: 0,0:34:15.23,0:34:17.23,Default,,0,0,0,,that they are not only a possibility
Dialogue: 0,0:34:17.23,0:34:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,,but a probability.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.28,0:34:21.28,Default,,0,0,0,,And eventually you realize
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.28,0:34:24.03,Default,,0,0,0,,that it is a certainty.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.03,0:34:25.03,Default,,0,0,0,,People who take a course
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.03,0:34:27.03,Default,,0,0,0,,to do the course of miracles
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.03,0:34:28.03,Default,,0,0,0,,are far more aware
Dialogue: 0,0:34:28.03,0:34:31.03,Default,,0,0,0,,of the presence of the miraculous
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.03,0:34:32.03,Default,,0,0,0,,and how to,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:32.03,0:34:35.75,Default,,0,0,0,,what to do in order to,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:35.75,0:34:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,,let's say,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.75,0:34:37.75,Default,,0,0,0,,facilitate the likelihood
Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.75,0:34:39.78,Default,,0,0,0,,of their emergence.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:39.78,0:34:40.78,Default,,0,0,0,,How many people here
Dialogue: 0,0:34:40.78,0:34:41.78,Default,,0,0,0,,have done the course?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:41.78,0:34:42.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.94,0:34:43.94,Default,,0,0,0,,So,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:43.94,0:34:45.94,Default,,0,0,0,,you all know what we're talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.94,0:34:49.21,Default,,0,0,0,,And the likelihood then
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.21,0:34:51.21,Default,,0,0,0,,is that when you can take,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:51.21,0:34:53.21,Default,,0,0,0,,when you change how you see a thing,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.21,0:34:55.21,Default,,0,0,0,,then you see it how it really is
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.21,0:34:56.21,Default,,0,0,0,,and how it really is
Dialogue: 0,0:34:56.21,0:34:58.21,Default,,0,0,0,,is miraculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:58.21,0:35:00.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't see the miraculous
Dialogue: 0,0:35:00.34,0:35:02.34,Default,,0,0,0,,until you start to become aware of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.34,0:35:04.73,Default,,0,0,0,,And therefore,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:04.73,0:35:05.73,Default,,0,0,0,,you don't ask
Dialogue: 0,0:35:05.73,0:35:07.73,Default,,0,0,0,,to have a certain thing done.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.73,0:35:10.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You ask for a change
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.73,0:35:13.59,Default,,0,0,0,,of how you're seeing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.59,0:35:14.59,Default,,0,0,0,,And when you see it differently,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:14.59,0:35:16.59,Default,,0,0,0,,you see that it wasn't that way
Dialogue: 0,0:35:16.59,0:35:17.59,Default,,0,0,0,,to begin with.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.59,0:35:19.84,Default,,0,0,0,,So the person who is bad
Dialogue: 0,0:35:19.84,0:35:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,doesn't suddenly become nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:21.84,0:35:23.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You just see the intrinsic
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.84,0:35:28.51,Default,,0,0,0,,niceness of the,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:28.51,0:35:30.51,Default,,0,0,0,,of the basic personality
Dialogue: 0,0:35:30.51,0:35:32.51,Default,,0,0,0,,that was obscured by
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.51,0:35:35.32,Default,,0,0,0,,some passing ripple.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:35.32,0:35:36.32,Default,,0,0,0,,The clinical experience
Dialogue: 0,0:35:36.32,0:35:38.32,Default,,0,0,0,,of a course is a miracle.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:38.32,0:35:40.01,Default,,0,0,0,,So,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.01,0:35:41.01,Default,,0,0,0,,you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.01,0:35:43.01,Default,,0,0,0,,we started groups here in Sedona.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:43.01,0:35:44.01,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact, I was the one
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.01,0:35:45.01,Default,,0,0,0,,that brought it to Sedona.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:45.01,0:35:46.01,Default,,0,0,0,,They didn't have the books
Dialogue: 0,0:35:46.01,0:35:47.11,Default,,0,0,0,,or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:47.11,0:35:50.11,Default,,0,0,0,,And we started at Unity Church
Dialogue: 0,0:35:50.11,0:35:52.71,Default,,0,0,0,,and they gave a sermon.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:52.71,0:35:54.71,Default,,0,0,0,,We had the company deliver the books
Dialogue: 0,0:35:54.71,0:35:56.71,Default,,0,0,0,,and I knew the printer of it
Dialogue: 0,0:35:56.71,0:35:58.71,Default,,0,0,0,,and I knew Helen and Bill
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.71,0:35:59.71,Default,,0,0,0,,and,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:59.71,0:36:02.03,Default,,0,0,0,,and Steinbergs.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:02.03,0:36:04.03,Default,,0,0,0,,And so we had it.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:04.03,0:36:05.30,Default,,0,0,0,,And I remember we had
Dialogue: 0,0:36:05.30,0:36:07.30,Default,,0,0,0,,over 100 people
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.30,0:36:08.30,Default,,0,0,0,,jammed up,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:08.30,0:36:10.30,Default,,0,0,0,,jammed the church that day.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.30,0:36:11.30,Default,,0,0,0,,And we ended up with,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:11.30,0:36:12.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I think,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:12.30,0:36:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,four groups
Dialogue: 0,0:36:13.30,0:36:14.30,Default,,0,0,0,,or six groups,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.30,0:36:15.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I forget how many,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:15.30,0:36:17.30,Default,,0,0,0,,out of the original people.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:17.30,0:36:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,,And those groups went
Dialogue: 0,0:36:18.30,0:36:19.30,Default,,0,0,0,,for many years
Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.30,0:36:21.30,Default,,0,0,0,,and some are still going.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:21.30,0:36:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Some of the groups we started,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.30,0:36:23.30,Default,,0,0,0,,and then we had
Dialogue: 0,0:36:23.30,0:36:25.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Jerry Jampolsky come
Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.30,0:36:27.48,Default,,0,0,0,,and lecture to us at
Dialogue: 0,0:36:27.48,0:36:29.48,Default,,0,0,0,,what was the old theater there.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.48,0:36:31.59,Default,,0,0,0,,We had a full house.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:31.59,0:36:32.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Three hundred people
Dialogue: 0,0:36:32.59,0:36:34.59,Default,,0,0,0,,filled up the movie theater
Dialogue: 0,0:36:34.59,0:36:36.94,Default,,0,0,0,,standing room only
Dialogue: 0,0:36:36.94,0:36:37.94,Default,,0,0,0,,to see Jerry
Dialogue: 0,0:36:37.94,0:36:40.94,Default,,0,0,0,,and the whole story of The Miraculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:40.94,0:36:41.94,Default,,0,0,0,,And of course his book
Dialogue: 0,0:36:41.94,0:36:43.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Love is Living Without Fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:43.94,0:36:44.94,Default,,0,0,0,,So,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:44.94,0:36:48.19,Default,,0,0,0,,The Miraculous has now become
Dialogue: 0,0:36:48.19,0:36:49.19,Default,,0,0,0,,much,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:49.19,0:36:50.19,Default,,0,0,0,,you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:50.19,0:36:51.19,Default,,0,0,0,,well known among
Dialogue: 0,0:36:51.19,0:36:53.19,Default,,0,0,0,,spiritually oriented people.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.19,0:36:55.19,Default,,0,0,0,,To the lay people in the world
Dialogue: 0,0:36:55.19,0:36:56.19,Default,,0,0,0,,it is still a
Dialogue: 0,0:36:56.19,0:36:57.19,Default,,0,0,0,,ooh, ooh, ooh
Dialogue: 0,0:36:57.19,0:36:58.57,Default,,0,0,0,,kind of a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.57,0:36:59.57,Default,,0,0,0,,And,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.57,0:37:00.57,Default,,0,0,0,,uh,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:00.57,0:37:01.57,Default,,0,0,0,,spooky.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:01.57,0:37:02.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Spooky and scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.57,0:37:03.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:03.63,0:37:04.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.63,0:37:05.63,Default,,0,0,0,,or very unlikely.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:05.63,0:37:06.63,Default,,0,0,0,,They say a miracle.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:06.63,0:37:07.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:07.63,0:37:09.03,Default,,0,0,0,,sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:09.03,0:37:10.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.03,0:37:11.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I say I've watched,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.03,0:37:12.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I get to some of
Dialogue: 0,0:37:12.03,0:37:13.03,Default,,0,0,0,,the miraculous
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.03,0:37:14.03,Default,,0,0,0,,that occurred around me
Dialogue: 0,0:37:14.03,0:37:15.03,Default,,0,0,0,,and I would watch
Dialogue: 0,0:37:15.03,0:37:16.03,Default,,0,0,0,,people witness it.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:16.03,0:37:17.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It was more fun
Dialogue: 0,0:37:17.03,0:37:18.03,Default,,0,0,0,,watching the people
Dialogue: 0,0:37:18.03,0:37:19.03,Default,,0,0,0,,witness it
Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.03,0:37:20.03,Default,,0,0,0,,than the miraculous experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:23.28,0:37:24.28,Default,,0,0,0,,So the miraculous
Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.28,0:37:25.28,Default,,0,0,0,,is a consequence
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.28,0:37:27.44,Default,,0,0,0,,of level of consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:27.44,0:37:28.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't see it
Dialogue: 0,0:37:28.44,0:37:29.44,Default,,0,0,0,,below level 200
Dialogue: 0,0:37:29.44,0:37:30.44,Default,,0,0,0,,and it's your
Dialogue: 0,0:37:30.44,0:37:31.44,Default,,0,0,0,,consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:37:31.44,0:37:32.44,Default,,0,0,0,,goes higher and higher
Dialogue: 0,0:37:32.44,0:37:33.44,Default,,0,0,0,,especially in the 500s.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:33.44,0:37:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,,In the 400s
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.44,0:37:35.44,Default,,0,0,0,,you're still dominated
Dialogue: 0,0:37:35.44,0:37:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,,considerably by reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:36.44,0:37:37.44,Default,,0,0,0,,But reason would tell you
Dialogue: 0,0:37:37.44,0:37:38.51,Default,,0,0,0,,if the miraculous
Dialogue: 0,0:37:38.51,0:37:39.51,Default,,0,0,0,,has been documented
Dialogue: 0,0:37:39.51,0:37:40.51,Default,,0,0,0,,by many witnesses
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.51,0:37:41.51,Default,,0,0,0,,throughout history
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.51,0:37:42.51,Default,,0,0,0,,it's very,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:42.51,0:37:43.51,Default,,0,0,0,,you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:43.51,0:37:44.51,Default,,0,0,0,,it's probably a likelihood.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:44.51,0:37:45.51,Default,,0,0,0,,But that would still
Dialogue: 0,0:37:45.51,0:37:46.51,Default,,0,0,0,,be reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:46.51,0:37:47.51,Default,,0,0,0,,But as you get
Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.51,0:37:48.51,Default,,0,0,0,,into the 500s
Dialogue: 0,0:37:48.51,0:37:50.36,Default,,0,0,0,,you get into
Dialogue: 0,0:37:50.36,0:37:51.36,Default,,0,0,0,,faith and love
Dialogue: 0,0:37:51.36,0:37:52.36,Default,,0,0,0,,and that tends
Dialogue: 0,0:37:52.36,0:37:53.36,Default,,0,0,0,,to precipitate
Dialogue: 0,0:37:53.36,0:37:54.36,Default,,0,0,0,,a deeper understanding
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.36,0:37:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,and awareness
Dialogue: 0,0:37:55.36,0:37:56.36,Default,,0,0,0,,and you begin
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.36,0:37:57.36,Default,,0,0,0,,to experience
Dialogue: 0,0:37:57.36,0:37:58.36,Default,,0,0,0,,the presence
Dialogue: 0,0:37:58.36,0:37:59.36,Default,,0,0,0,,of the miraculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:59.36,0:38:00.36,Default,,0,0,0,,So,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:00.36,0:38:01.36,Default,,0,0,0,,the miraculous
Dialogue: 0,0:38:01.36,0:38:02.36,Default,,0,0,0,,is both experienced
Dialogue: 0,0:38:02.36,0:38:03.36,Default,,0,0,0,,and witnessed
Dialogue: 0,0:38:03.36,0:38:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,at a consequent
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.92,0:38:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,,level of consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:05.92,0:38:06.92,Default,,0,0,0,,So,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.92,0:38:07.92,Default,,0,0,0,,a person
Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.92,0:38:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,who's below 200
Dialogue: 0,0:38:08.92,0:38:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,how in the world
Dialogue: 0,0:38:09.92,0:38:11.90,Default,,0,0,0,,did they get above?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.90,0:38:12.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Well,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:12.90,0:38:13.90,Default,,0,0,0,,by intention.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:13.90,0:38:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,,By intention.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:14.90,0:38:15.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Because,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:15.90,0:38:18.03,Default,,0,0,0,,because the Emperor
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.03,0:38:19.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Constantine
Dialogue: 0,0:38:19.03,0:38:20.03,Default,,0,0,0,,was at 195.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:20.03,0:38:21.03,Default,,0,0,0,,He was at 195.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:21.03,0:38:22.03,Default,,0,0,0,,So,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:22.03,0:38:23.34,Default,,0,0,0,,how come
Dialogue: 0,0:38:23.34,0:38:25.40,Default,,0,0,0,,a great miracle
Dialogue: 0,0:38:25.40,0:38:26.40,Default,,0,0,0,,occurred
Dialogue: 0,0:38:26.40,0:38:27.40,Default,,0,0,0,,at 195?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:27.40,0:38:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Well,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:28.40,0:38:29.40,Default,,0,0,0,,it's because
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.40,0:38:30.98,Default,,0,0,0,,the Emperor
Dialogue: 0,0:38:30.98,0:38:31.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Constantine
Dialogue: 0,0:38:31.98,0:38:32.98,Default,,0,0,0,,was at 195.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:32.98,0:38:33.98,Default,,0,0,0,,So,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:33.98,0:38:34.98,Default,,0,0,0,,the miracle
Dialogue: 0,0:38:34.98,0:38:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,occurred at 195
Dialogue: 0,0:38:35.98,0:38:36.98,Default,,0,0,0,,as I explained.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:36.98,0:38:37.98,Default,,0,0,0,,He was at 195.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:37.98,0:38:38.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Then he said,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:38.98,0:38:39.98,Default,,0,0,0,,oh God,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:39.98,0:38:41.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:41.01,0:38:42.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I pray to you
Dialogue: 0,0:38:42.01,0:38:43.01,Default,,0,0,0,,for a sign.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:43.01,0:38:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Bang.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:45.40,0:38:46.40,Default,,0,0,0,,People have been
Dialogue: 0,0:38:46.40,0:38:47.40,Default,,0,0,0,,praying for a sign
Dialogue: 0,0:38:47.40,0:38:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,ever since.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.40,0:38:51.46,Default,,0,0,0,,But you'll,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:51.46,0:38:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,when you examine it
Dialogue: 0,0:38:52.46,0:38:53.46,Default,,0,0,0,,you'll find
Dialogue: 0,0:38:53.46,0:38:54.46,Default,,0,0,0,,that's attempted control.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.46,0:38:55.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You're trying
Dialogue: 0,0:38:55.46,0:38:56.55,Default,,0,0,0,,to outline.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:56.55,0:38:57.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Telling God
Dialogue: 0,0:38:57.55,0:38:58.55,Default,,0,0,0,,what to do
Dialogue: 0,0:38:58.55,0:38:59.55,Default,,0,0,0,,is called outlining
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.55,0:39:00.55,Default,,0,0,0,,and,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:00.55,0:39:01.65,Default,,0,0,0,,you tell God
Dialogue: 0,0:39:01.65,0:39:02.65,Default,,0,0,0,,not only
Dialogue: 0,0:39:02.65,0:39:03.65,Default,,0,0,0,,what you want
Dialogue: 0,0:39:03.65,0:39:04.65,Default,,0,0,0,,to happen
Dialogue: 0,0:39:04.65,0:39:05.65,Default,,0,0,0,,but also
Dialogue: 0,0:39:05.65,0:39:06.65,Default,,0,0,0,,what you want
Dialogue: 0,0:39:06.65,0:39:07.65,Default,,0,0,0,,to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:07.65,0:39:08.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:08.65,0:39:09.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I,
