Dialogue: 0,0:39:59.78,0:40:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:02.40,0:40:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.40,0:40:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:04.40,0:40:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,12-step groups, of course. The miraculous is commonplace in every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.92,0:40:25.21,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a skeptic that wrote something very negative about the miraculous,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:25.21,0:40:32.11,Default,,0,0,0,,consciousness, all kind of them. And I would say to a person like that,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:32.11,0:40:38.26,Default,,0,0,0,,do you know that there's like, I don't know how many, 3 million members of Alcoholics Anonymous right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.26,0:40:42.26,Default,,0,0,0,,There's over a million recovered alcoholics walking all over the globe?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:42.26,0:40:45.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see, there's over a million. You don't have to get up all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:45.67,0:40:52.55,Default,,0,0,0,,There's over a million recovered alcoholics. Two million. One and a half million.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:52.55,0:40:58.73,Default,,0,0,0,,One and three quarters million. That's close enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:58.73,0:41:03.73,Default,,0,0,0,,A million and a half hopeless victims of a progressive deteriorating disease
Dialogue: 0,0:41:03.73,0:41:08.73,Default,,0,0,0,,that eventually causes brain damage and hallucinations and convulsions.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:08.73,0:41:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,And you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:09.80,0:41:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,you die with a wet brain.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:11.80,0:41:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I remember at autopsy we'd take off the top of the skull with a little saw
Dialogue: 0,0:41:16.92,0:41:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,and you could smell alcohol in the whole room from the person's brain.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:20.92,0:41:26.34,Default,,0,0,0,,A hopeless progressive condition. Least of progressive insanity,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:26.34,0:41:32.59,Default,,0,0,0,,grand mal convulsions, and finally you get put away with a wet brain.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:32.59,0:41:37.59,Default,,0,0,0,,A completely hopeless condition. There was never, hardly ever, very,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:37.59,0:41:40.59,Default,,0,0,0,,just once in a while in history it would occur.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:40.59,0:41:45.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Only if the person threw themselves devotedly into some kind of a spiritual organization.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:45.59,0:41:52.51,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's what Carl Jung told Roland, who was a hopeless alcoholic.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:52.51,0:42:00.42,Default,,0,0,0,,And Roland saw Carl Jung and Jung, he was in pretty good shape, came back to America.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:00.42,0:42:06.11,Default,,0,0,0,,But then Roland got drunk again and came back to see Carl Jung.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:06.11,0:42:11.82,Default,,0,0,0,,And Jung, thank God for his honesty, said,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:11.82,0:42:17.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Alas, there are some things that neither my art nor my science can help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:17.82,0:42:22.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Neither my art nor science.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:22.36,0:42:26.36,Default,,0,0,0,,However, it has occurred occasionally throughout history.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:26.36,0:42:31.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It has been recorded that people have recovered from this grave and hopeless progressive disease
Dialogue: 0,0:42:31.36,0:42:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,who threw themselves wholeheartedly into religious or spiritual programs.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:36.48,0:42:43.42,Default,,0,0,0,,And Roland, who was an atheist at the time I suppose, went back dejectedly.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:43.42,0:42:46.63,Default,,0,0,0,,But he sought out the Oxford groups.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:46.63,0:42:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,And the Oxford groups followed certain steps, which are the basic steps of AA,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:52.86,0:42:56.09,Default,,0,0,0,,or the 12-step recovery group.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:56.09,0:43:01.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Roland recovered, and then it got transmitted to Ebby.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:01.53,0:43:08.28,Default,,0,0,0,,And Ebby told Bill Wilson.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:08.28,0:43:10.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Bill Wilson was a skeptic and an atheist, and he said,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:10.28,0:43:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't got any time for all that God business. Go away.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:14.28,0:43:16.28,Default,,0,0,0,,But things got worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:16.28,0:43:19.67,Default,,0,0,0,,He was in and out of Towns Hospital in New York City.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:19.67,0:43:21.67,Default,,0,0,0,,And his wife, Lois, was in despair.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:21.67,0:43:26.07,Default,,0,0,0,,The doctor said, prepare for his death.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:26.07,0:43:30.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, then Bill did listen to him and changed his mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:30.36,0:43:34.71,Default,,0,0,0,,And he took a great leap.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:34.71,0:43:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,And Bill prayed to God.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:37.00,0:43:42.78,Default,,0,0,0,,And then the miraculous happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:42.78,0:43:45.42,Default,,0,0,0,,The drum lit up.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:45.42,0:44:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,That was a miracle.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:05.76,0:44:08.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It changed the lives of millions of people worldwide.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:08.76,0:44:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,And the 12-step groups.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:10.80,0:44:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Out of them emerged all the other 12-step groups, recovery groups.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:14.80,0:44:20.07,Default,,0,0,0,,And group therapy itself came out of AA.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:20.07,0:44:27.69,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's one of the most powerful spiritual organizations in our culture.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:27.69,0:44:29.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Because it's silent.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:29.69,0:44:31.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It's invisible.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:31.69,0:44:37.69,Default,,0,0,0,,And it merely influences all of society by virtue of its energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:37.69,0:44:40.69,Default,,0,0,0,,And not by virtue of buildings or edifices.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:40.69,0:44:42.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Or rich and famous people.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:42.69,0:44:44.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't see any TV ads for AA.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:44.69,0:44:46.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't see any billboards.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:46.69,0:44:52.30,Default,,0,0,0,,And because of anonymity at the level of the press, etc.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:52.30,0:44:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't see them getting up and saying, I'm so-and-so.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:57.48,0:45:03.92,Default,,0,0,0,,So the very famous 12-step groups were then.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:03.92,0:45:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,So I have to say to the skeptic who, in the skeptic dictionary, who poos faith.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:08.92,0:45:11.92,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you explain the recovery of one and a half million people?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:11.92,0:45:15.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Alive today.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:15.92,0:45:18.92,Default,,0,0,0,,All given up as hopeless and incurable.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:18.92,0:45:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,So the power of faith, then, is sufficient to precipitate the miraculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:25.96,0:45:28.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't cause it.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:28.59,0:45:31.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Powerful spiritual energy is context.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:31.59,0:45:38.59,Default,,0,0,0,,And within that context, then, likelihood becomes actuality if it's karmically propitious.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:38.59,0:45:40.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Karmically propitious.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:40.59,0:45:44.76,Default,,0,0,0,,So lower mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:44.76,0:45:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the skeptic's mind at 155.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:49.76,0:45:52.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Has an intrinsic limitation.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:52.80,0:45:56.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Very intrinsic limitation.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:56.57,0:46:01.98,Default,,0,0,0,,And therefore, there's no point in being angry at them or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:01.98,0:46:05.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just that they cannot see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:05.21,0:46:10.21,Default,,0,0,0,,There are some unfortunates who are born with a limitation.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:10.21,0:46:15.55,Default,,0,0,0,,And the fifth chapter of the book Alcoholics Anonymous states.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:15.55,0:46:24.69,Default,,0,0,0,,There are those unfortunates who apparently have been born with an incapacity to be honest with themselves and others.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:24.69,0:46:25.69,Default,,0,0,0,,They cannot help it.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:25.69,0:46:29.65,Default,,0,0,0,,They were born that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:29.65,0:46:32.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:32.19,0:46:35.57,Default,,0,0,0,,They were born that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:35.57,0:46:38.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, they came into this lifetime.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:38.57,0:46:42.57,Default,,0,0,0,,At a very low energy calibration level.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:42.57,0:46:47.63,Default,,0,0,0,,And they're here more or less in the kindergarten.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:47.63,0:46:54.63,Default,,0,0,0,,And just learning the very first things about being honest and truthful and trying to be nice to people.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:54.63,0:47:00.32,Default,,0,0,0,,There are people to whom that is quite foreign.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:00.32,0:47:01.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:01.32,0:47:04.75,Default,,0,0,0,,So the skeptic, then, we can expect.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:04.75,0:47:08.75,Default,,0,0,0,,If we talk about miracles, you're going to try to out every skeptic.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:08.75,0:47:14.75,Default,,0,0,0,,And they will get very busy and create marvelous machines that can imitate a miracle.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:14.75,0:47:16.75,Default,,0,0,0,,And if you can do it by machinery.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:16.75,0:47:18.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore, the reality couldn't have happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:18.75,0:47:21.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Because you can see I can make it look like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:21.90,0:47:23.90,Default,,0,0,0,,And you see them on TV every once in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:23.90,0:47:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,They all have the same attitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:25.90,0:47:28.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I can tell the minute they come on the screen.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:28.90,0:47:30.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Where their head is at.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:30.90,0:47:32.90,Default,,0,0,0,,And what they're about, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:32.90,0:47:38.90,Default,,0,0,0,,They put together elaborate laboratory equipment and lighting and electronic controls and all.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:38.90,0:47:39.90,Default,,0,0,0,,And make it sizzle like.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:39.90,0:47:41.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you see I can make it sizzle like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:41.90,0:47:44.03,Default,,0,0,0,,So it couldn't have, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:44.03,0:47:47.03,Default,,0,0,0,,So it couldn't have sizzled in the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:47.03,0:47:48.38,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:48.38,0:47:50.38,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's the limitation of lower mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:50.38,0:47:54.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Unfortunates who are born that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:54.21,0:47:57.21,Default,,0,0,0,,They're still at an early level of evolution, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:57.21,0:48:00.21,Default,,0,0,0,,And they deserve sympathy.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:00.21,0:48:01.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Sympathy.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:01.21,0:48:04.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Rather than to revile them.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:04.21,0:48:07.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:07.69,0:48:12.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:12.15,0:48:17.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Miraculous is consequent to the level of consciousness of the observer.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:17.71,0:48:20.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Of the observer.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:20.48,0:48:24.55,Default,,0,0,0,,So the phenomena are witnessed.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:24.55,0:48:25.55,Default,,0,0,0,,They've happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:25.55,0:48:26.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:26.55,0:48:27.55,Default,,0,0,0,,As I say in our travels.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:27.55,0:48:28.63,Default,,0,0,0,,They happen many a time.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:28.63,0:48:33.63,Default,,0,0,0,,We're in some foreign country with some group that we're speaking with or for.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:33.63,0:48:41.05,Default,,0,0,0,,And they will bring somebody over and sit them right across from the table from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:41.05,0:48:45.32,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm wondering why did they bring that person.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:45.32,0:48:49.82,Default,,0,0,0,,And then all of a sudden I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:49.82,0:48:52.82,Default,,0,0,0,,And I say, oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:52.82,0:48:54.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I see what it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:54.82,0:48:55.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:55.82,0:48:57.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I don't think in terms of miracles.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:57.82,0:48:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I just.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:58.82,0:49:01.82,Default,,0,0,0,,The phenomena that are occurring are all miraculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:01.82,0:49:05.82,Default,,0,0,0,,So I don't separate it out that this is miraculous and that is not.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:05.82,0:49:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You see.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:06.96,0:49:10.96,Default,,0,0,0,,But apparently that energy with the right karmic preparation.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:10.96,0:49:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,The group brings her here.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:11.96,0:49:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,,And now this side of her brain which was numb and wouldn't work.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:14.96,0:49:15.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Works and everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:15.96,0:49:19.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:19.05,0:49:24.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It's consequent to the level of consciousness of the observer.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:24.17,0:49:25.17,Default,,0,0,0,,The miraculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:25.17,0:49:27.40,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a constant.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:27.40,0:49:29.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Creation and evolution.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:29.40,0:49:39.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Creation as evolution.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:39.17,0:49:43.17,Default,,0,0,0,,The presence of creation is continuously present.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:43.17,0:49:45.17,Default,,0,0,0,,And the form that.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:45.17,0:49:48.61,Default,,0,0,0,,The form that it takes.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:48.61,0:49:50.61,Default,,0,0,0,,The form that creation takes.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:50.61,0:49:55.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Is evolutionary from the viewpoint of the witness.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:55.19,0:50:01.44,Default,,0,0,0,,The witness thinks that it's out there as evolutionary.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:01.44,0:50:03.69,Default,,0,0,0,,So divinity.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:03.69,0:50:04.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Divinity.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:04.69,0:50:06.69,Default,,0,0,0,,When it expresses itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:06.69,0:50:09.48,Default,,0,0,0,,In this dimension.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:09.48,0:50:10.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Becomes.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:10.48,0:50:11.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Evolutionary.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:11.48,0:50:19.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course we used to always start out these lectures recapitulating the evolution of consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:19.09,0:50:23.09,Default,,0,0,0,,To give it just an overall context so that it becomes obvious.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:23.09,0:50:26.48,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's quite obvious that.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:26.48,0:50:29.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Consciousness itself and its expression is evolutionary.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:29.48,0:50:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,,From lower to higher and higher forms.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:34.44,0:50:38.01,Default,,0,0,0,,And finally you get the prefrontal cortex.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:38.01,0:50:39.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you're in trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:39.01,0:50:42.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Now you can think.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:42.01,0:50:46.05,Default,,0,0,0,,God help the world now.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:46.05,0:50:48.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You can think.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:48.15,0:50:50.15,Default,,0,0,0,,So when you give an animal.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:50.15,0:50:53.23,Default,,0,0,0,,When you give some intelligent human.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:53.23,0:50:55.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Who calibrates below 200.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:55.23,0:50:57.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You give them a prefrontal cortex.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:57.23,0:50:59.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Gray matter with which to think.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:59.23,0:51:03.26,Default,,0,0,0,,He's now a very dangerous animal.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:03.26,0:51:06.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Energized by wickedness.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:06.57,0:51:08.57,Default,,0,0,0,,And now with the know how.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:08.57,0:51:10.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Of how to put it into nuclear physics.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:10.71,0:51:11.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Or whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:11.71,0:51:12.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Form.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:12.71,0:51:13.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It can be put in.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:13.71,0:51:14.71,Default,,0,0,0,,So.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:14.71,0:51:15.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Miraculous is.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:15.71,0:51:18.28,Default,,0,0,0,,The miraculous is constant.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:18.28,0:51:19.28,Default,,0,0,0,,So if.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:19.28,0:51:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Creation.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:20.28,0:51:21.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Then.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:21.28,0:51:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,If.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:22.30,0:51:23.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Creation takes the form of evolution.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:23.30,0:51:24.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Evolution is the constant emergence of potentiality.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:24.30,0:51:25.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Into action.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:25.30,0:51:26.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Actuality.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:26.30,0:51:27.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:27.30,0:51:28.82,Default,,0,0,0,,All of creation is continuously.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:28.82,0:51:29.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Miraculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:29.82,0:51:30.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You live.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:30.82,0:51:31.82,Default,,0,0,0,,As.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:31.82,0:51:32.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You live.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:32.98,0:51:33.98,Default,,0,0,0,,As.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:33.98,0:51:34.98,Default,,0,0,0,,As.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:34.98,0:51:36.13,Default,,0,0,0,,As.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:36.13,0:51:37.13,Default,,0,0,0,,As.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:37.13,0:51:38.13,Default,,0,0,0,,As.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:38.13,0:51:39.13,Default,,0,0,0,,As.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:39.13,0:51:40.13,Default,,0,0,0,,As.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:40.13,0:51:41.13,Default,,0,0,0,,As.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:41.13,0:51:44.21,Default,,0,0,0,,As.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:44.21,0:51:45.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You live.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:45.21,0:51:46.21,Default,,0,0,0,,As.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:46.21,0:51:47.21,Default,,0,0,0,,A consequence.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:47.21,0:51:48.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Of the miraculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:48.21,0:51:49.21,Default,,0,0,0,,In the presence.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:49.21,0:51:50.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Of the miraculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:50.63,0:51:51.63,Default,,0,0,0,,And.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:51.63,0:51:52.63,Default,,0,0,0,,At.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:52.63,0:51:53.63,Default,,0,0,0,,A certain level of consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:53.63,0:51:54.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You become aware that the miraculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:54.63,0:51:55.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Is a constant.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:55.63,0:51:56.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not an infrequent.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:56.63,0:51:57.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not rare.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:57.63,0:51:58.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not something you separate.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:58.63,0:51:59.63,Default,,0,0,0,,From real life.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:59.63,0:52:00.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It is real life.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:00.63,0:52:01.63,Default,,0,0,0,,To watch this.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:01.63,0:52:02.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Emerge.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:02.63,0:52:03.63,Default,,0,0,0,,We've.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:03.63,0:52:04.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Got.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:04.63,0:52:05.96,Default,,0,0,0,,A.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:05.96,0:52:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:06.96,0:52:08.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Bulb.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:08.17,0:52:09.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Of.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:09.17,0:52:10.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Some.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:10.17,0:52:11.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:11.17,0:52:12.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Of.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:12.17,0:52:13.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Flower.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:13.17,0:52:14.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Bulb.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:14.17,0:52:15.17,Default,,0,0,0,,At Home.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:15.17,0:52:20.67,Default,,0,0,0,,bigger and bigger and bigger, and now it's just splendiferous. What's the name
Dialogue: 0,0:52:20.67,0:52:29.09,Default,,0,0,0,,of that crazy big bulb we got? Yeah, well it's just splendiferous. It goes from
Dialogue: 0,0:52:29.09,0:52:32.57,Default,,0,0,0,,just a dopey looking bulb and then every day gets more interesting,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:32.57,0:52:42.19,Default,,0,0,0,,and then finally it's just, wow, Christmas time. I just think they're just
Dialogue: 0,0:52:42.19,0:52:52.71,Default,,0,0,0,,wonderful. So you see the miraculous of the amaryllis. Amaryllis? Amaryllis, my honey.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:52.71,0:52:59.75,Default,,0,0,0,,That's my amaryllis. I fell in love with amaryllis, I just had to sing that
Dialogue: 0,0:52:59.75,0:53:09.05,Default,,0,0,0,,beautiful flower song. You are so pretty in the window. I was glad I'd wear an
Dialogue: 0,0:53:09.05,0:53:13.21,Default,,0,0,0,,amaryllis over my ear, and every day it gets bigger and bigger.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:13.21,0:53:13.71,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:14.15,0:53:27.09,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, so the miraculous is an intrinsic quality. It's statistical
Dialogue: 0,0:53:27.09,0:53:32.63,Default,,0,0,0,,likelihood is what hangs people up, and the other thing that holds them up is
Dialogue: 0,0:53:32.63,0:53:45.23,Default,,0,0,0,,being literal and linear. People in this room would not even be alive today
Dialogue: 0,0:53:45.23,0:53:50.19,Default,,0,0,0,,were it not for the miraculous in their lives. Resist. Everyone here is alive
Dialogue: 0,0:53:50.19,0:53:54.13,Default,,0,0,0,,because of the miraculous in your lives. You may think of some stunning incident
Dialogue: 0,0:53:54.13,0:54:01.03,Default,,0,0,0,,that sounds good to your grandmother, but it's the car that almost hit you in the road and it didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:01.03,0:54:07.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll just witness, I'm going to recall a memory of a...
Dialogue: 0,0:54:07.01,0:54:12.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to jump up all the time, honey. What I'm holding in mind was miraculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:12.05,0:54:19.67,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, I was going down 89A. I used to go over the Mingus Mountain for about 12 years
Dialogue: 0,0:54:19.67,0:54:26.51,Default,,0,0,0,,because there was a girl's recovery house there, and they didn't have any doctors, so I went over.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:26.51,0:54:36.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it, my not going over the cliff at that time was miraculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:36.82,0:54:43.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Resist. My God, I came so close. It's 5,000 feet down. It's a torturous road.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:43.94,0:54:49.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It was snow on it, and you come around the side. Anyway, I didn't go over the side.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:49.84,0:54:59.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I forgot what I was talking about now.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:59.32,0:55:12.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm? Huh? Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:13.51,0:55:22.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Impersonally. All right, so the miraculous is a phenomena that's witnessed and not caused.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:22.32,0:55:29.94,Default,,0,0,0,,So there's nobody who causes miracles. Therefore, it doesn't make sense to run down to South America
Dialogue: 0,0:55:29.94,0:55:38.80,Default,,0,0,0,,to see the God-man who performs miracles all the time. They go down there by the thousands
Dialogue: 0,0:55:38.80,0:55:47.15,Default,,0,0,0,,because there is no person causing a miracle. They're phenomena that happen of their own.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:47.15,0:55:48.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It's impersonal.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:48.15,0:55:53.73,Default,,0,0,0,,So healings are really, a lot of times we think healings are spontaneous,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:53.73,0:55:59.59,Default,,0,0,0,,but they're really the consequence of your level of consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:59.59,0:56:05.59,Default,,0,0,0,,They're the consequence of the effect of prayer, which we can get into later.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:05.59,0:56:12.71,Default,,0,0,0,,So the miraculous is abused by promoters for fame and money, and India, the holy men of India,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:12.71,0:56:19.63,Default,,0,0,0,,the classic ones, they have it down to expert.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:19.63,0:56:20.63,Default,,0,0,0,,The skeptics caught.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:20.63,0:56:21.63,Default,,0,0,0,,This is what I'm thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:21.63,0:56:27.63,Default,,0,0,0,,They finally caught it on a photograph how he was performing the miracle.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:27.63,0:56:29.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess it was all over the internet.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:29.63,0:56:32.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, the holy men of India are experts.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:32.92,0:56:39.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Many of them are expert at simulating the miraculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:39.28,0:56:43.48,Default,,0,0,0,,And don't underrate the expertise.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:43.48,0:56:46.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been perfected over thousands of years.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:46.57,0:56:52.28,Default,,0,0,0,,And when you meet a real miracle-performing holy man,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:52.28,0:56:59.32,Default,,0,0,0,,it's entrancing.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:59.32,0:57:02.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You're sure you just saw the real thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:02.32,0:57:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You're sure you just saw the real thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:06.80,0:57:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Very great in expertise.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:09.80,0:57:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,No person is performing the miracles.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:14.32,0:57:21.65,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll go to the Heisenberg principle, and then I'll give you some of my own personal experiences.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:21.65,0:57:24.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Contribution of the Heisenberg principle, of course,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:24.65,0:57:26.65,Default,,0,0,0,,makes the whole thing scientifically,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:26.65,0:57:30.13,Default,,0,0,0,,scientifically possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:30.13,0:57:34.17,Default,,0,0,0,,The power of intention.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:34.17,0:57:39.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It wasn't really until quantum mechanics and the Heisenberg principle
Dialogue: 0,0:57:39.71,0:57:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,that there was a crossover between the linear and the non-linear domain.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:48.96,0:57:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,And now we see the power of intention.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:50.96,0:57:59.34,Default,,0,0,0,,So everyone hoping for and praying for someone's recovery
Dialogue: 0,0:57:59.34,0:58:02.34,Default,,0,0,0,,increases the likelihood of that occurrence.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:02.34,0:58:03.34,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't cause it.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:03.34,0:58:06.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It does not determine it.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:06.01,0:58:10.01,Default,,0,0,0,,And if it is karmically not the right time,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:10.01,0:58:12.01,Default,,0,0,0,,it's not going to happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:12.01,0:58:13.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:13.46,0:58:19.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Because every event is synchronized with everything else in creation.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:19.28,0:58:23.28,Default,,0,0,0,,And your healing from something might disrupt something else.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:23.28,0:58:27.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Say, oh dear God, please don't let me die from so-and-so.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:27.73,0:58:29.73,Default,,0,0,0,,The question is, why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:32.34,0:58:36.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You'd rather be crushed by a truck, maybe?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:37.32,0:58:50.44,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, because everything in the universe
Dialogue: 0,0:58:50.44,0:58:52.44,Default,,0,0,0,,is intertwined with everything else.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:52.44,0:58:56.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What some people are doing is praying intensely
Dialogue: 0,0:58:56.30,0:58:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,to try and change that synchronicity.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:59.30,0:59:02.53,Default,,0,0,0,,But you see, if this thumb doesn't turn,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:02.53,0:59:04.53,Default,,0,0,0,,then the hand can't open.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:04.53,0:59:06.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore, what you're praying for
Dialogue: 0,0:59:06.53,0:59:11.53,Default,,0,0,0,,would be the antithesis of the design of creation altogether.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:11.53,0:59:13.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You're asking for something
Dialogue: 0,0:59:13.53,0:59:17.13,Default,,0,0,0,,that would not be fortuitous.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:17.13,0:59:20.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Healings, for instance.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:20.71,0:59:25.55,Default,,0,0,0,,What is served by suffering?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:25.55,0:59:29.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, one thing it undoes a lot of bad karma, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:29.55,0:59:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, the last pope held up the dignity of suffering.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:34.00,0:59:38.55,Default,,0,0,0,,He did not give us a consciousness explanation for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:38.55,0:59:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,But sort of intuitive we got
Dialogue: 0,0:59:41.80,0:59:45.98,Default,,0,0,0,,that it's a propitiation for sin.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:45.98,0:59:47.98,Default,,0,0,0,,And because of his stature,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:47.98,0:59:49.98,Default,,0,0,0,,he was to some degree
Dialogue: 0,0:59:49.98,0:59:54.44,Default,,0,0,0,,taking on the propitiation of the sin and suffering
Dialogue: 0,0:59:54.44,0:59:58.44,Default,,0,0,0,,of others to the greatest degree he could
Dialogue: 0,0:59:58.44,1:00:00.44,Default,,0,0,0,,at his level of consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:00.44,1:00:05.48,Default,,0,0,0,,So, the willingness to surrender
Dialogue: 0,1:00:05.48,1:00:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,to whatever the consequence may be
Dialogue: 0,1:00:10.00,1:00:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,seems paradoxical.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:12.00,1:00:16.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You say, well, if I give up wanting that person to recover
Dialogue: 0,1:00:16.03,1:00:18.03,Default,,0,0,0,,or wanting myself to recover,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:18.03,1:00:20.03,Default,,0,0,0,,then how would I recover?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:20.03,1:00:21.63,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:21.63,1:00:22.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Because you surrender it
Dialogue: 0,1:00:22.63,1:00:23.63,Default,,0,0,0,,to the will of God,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:23.63,1:00:26.63,Default,,0,0,0,,and then the karmic propensities,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:26.63,1:00:28.63,Default,,0,0,0,,it will manifest in a certain way
Dialogue: 0,1:00:28.63,1:00:30.63,Default,,0,0,0,,or it will not manifest.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:30.63,1:00:36.53,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:36.53,1:00:37.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Subjective witnessing.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:37.53,1:00:39.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, well, we'll get to that last.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:39.53,1:00:40.53,Default,,0,0,0,,What time is it now?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:40.53,1:00:43.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Fifteen more minutes.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:43.32,1:00:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:44.32,1:00:46.53,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:46.53,1:00:47.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:47.53,1:00:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you know, I was a physician.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:49.80,1:00:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I still am.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:50.80,1:00:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Practiced for 50 years.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:52.86,1:00:55.86,Default,,0,0,0,,And so, healing versus treating,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:55.86,1:00:58.86,Default,,0,0,0,,to me, is quite an interesting subject.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:58.86,1:00:59.86,Default,,0,0,0,,And we're going to have
Dialogue: 0,1:00:59.86,1:01:03.86,Default,,0,0,0,,a special restorative medicine conference here.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:03.86,1:01:05.86,Default,,0,0,0,,They're going to come here to Sedona.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:05.86,1:01:07.86,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm going to speak one morning, in fact,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:07.86,1:01:09.86,Default,,0,0,0,,next October.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:09.86,1:01:15.01,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'll be speaking more about that particularly.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:15.01,1:01:21.67,Default,,0,0,0,,In this experience,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:21.67,1:01:31.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I had a chance to experience many things
Dialogue: 0,1:01:31.46,1:01:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,in both the medical and the non-medical fields,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:35.80,1:01:37.80,Default,,0,0,0,,experientially.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:37.80,1:01:40.07,Default,,0,0,0,,So, we give,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:40.07,1:01:44.57,Default,,0,0,0,,testimony to the miracles
Dialogue: 0,1:01:44.57,1:01:46.57,Default,,0,0,0,,that we have witnessed and experienced
Dialogue: 0,1:01:46.57,1:01:48.59,Default,,0,0,0,,within our own life.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:48.59,1:01:49.59,Default,,0,0,0,,As we say,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:49.59,1:01:53.59,Default,,0,0,0,,everyone here is alive because of a miracle,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:53.59,1:01:57.30,Default,,0,0,0,,because of many miracles.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:57.30,1:02:00.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just that you have not recognized them.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:00.30,1:02:02.90,Default,,0,0,0,,So, I'll just give you an obvious example.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:02.90,1:02:06.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I was going down 89A about 65 miles an hour.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:06.90,1:02:08.90,Default,,0,0,0,,In those days, it wasn't four lane.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:08.90,1:02:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It was only two lane.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:09.90,1:02:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,,And it was early in the morning.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:13.48,1:02:15.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, 10 to 7.30.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:15.92,1:02:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Everybody's coming to work.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:17.92,1:02:21.09,Default,,0,0,0,,So, all the heavy traffic was coming up from Cottonwood.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:21.09,1:02:22.09,Default,,0,0,0,,So, as I'm going south,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:22.09,1:02:24.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm in the right-hand lane.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:24.09,1:02:28.34,Default,,0,0,0,,And the left-hand lane was solid cars all the way down.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:28.34,1:02:30.53,Default,,0,0,0,,In my lane, there was nobody.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:30.53,1:02:33.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I had this lane all to myself.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:33.53,1:02:36.53,Default,,0,0,0,,And the other lane was jammed.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:36.53,1:02:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,All of a sudden,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:37.92,1:02:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,we're going 65, 70.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:39.92,1:02:42.92,Default,,0,0,0,,All of a sudden, the car pulled out.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:42.92,1:02:44.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd say a quarter mile down.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:44.28,1:02:48.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Pulled into my lane, coming straight at me.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:48.28,1:02:50.28,Default,,0,0,0,,There's only two cars in this lane now.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:50.28,1:02:52.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going south, 70.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:52.28,1:02:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,And he's coming north, 65 or so.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:55.28,1:02:57.63,Default,,0,0,0,,And as he gets closer and closer,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:57.63,1:03:01.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I figure he's going to pull into line any minute now.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:01.63,1:03:03.63,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm watching as he gets closer and closer,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:03.63,1:03:05.63,Default,,0,0,0,,and I can see he can't get into line.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:05.63,1:03:07.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Nobody's going to let him in.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:07.63,1:03:09.63,Default,,0,0,0,,He tries to pull the right.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:09.63,1:03:11.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Nobody's going to let him in.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:11.98,1:03:13.98,Default,,0,0,0,,And we were headed for a head-on.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:13.98,1:03:16.90,Default,,0,0,0,,65.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:16.90,1:03:19.90,Default,,0,0,0,,He was going 65 or 70, and so was I.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:19.90,1:03:21.90,Default,,0,0,0,,So two cars, a head-on at 70 degrees.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:21.90,1:03:23.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It would have made a splash, I'll tell you.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:28.09,1:03:29.09,Default,,0,0,0,,So I prepared to go,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:29.09,1:03:32.09,Default,,0,0,0,,and I just surrendered the whole situation to God.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:32.09,1:03:34.19,Default,,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 0,1:03:34.19,1:03:37.21,Default,,0,0,0,,All of a sudden, this oncoming car pulled off.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:37.21,1:03:40.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Pulled off the highway onto the side.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:40.21,1:03:42.21,Default,,0,0,0,,And sort of tipped over like this,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:42.21,1:03:44.21,Default,,0,0,0,,somebody in the ditch, you know.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:44.21,1:03:45.21,Default,,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 0,1:03:45.21,1:03:47.40,Default,,0,0,0,,So I drove on.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:47.40,1:03:49.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I looked in the rearview mirror,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:49.40,1:03:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,and that guy stayed there a long time
Dialogue: 0,1:03:51.40,1:03:53.40,Default,,0,0,0,,off the side of the road.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:57.44,1:03:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,He did not just quickly recover
Dialogue: 0,1:03:59.44,1:04:01.44,Default,,0,0,0,,and go back into traffic.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:01.44,1:04:03.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I looked a couple of minutes down the thing.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:03.44,1:04:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I could still see way back.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:05.44,1:04:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,He was still recovering.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:10.00,1:04:12.03,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, so...
Dialogue: 0,1:04:12.03,1:04:14.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, the person would say,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:14.03,1:04:17.51,Default,,0,0,0,,what would the average mind think of that incident?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:17.51,1:04:20.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:20.03,1:04:22.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Lucky, eh? Lucky, eh?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:22.03,1:04:23.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you were lucky.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:23.03,1:04:25.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You pulled over at the last minute, eh?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:25.03,1:04:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, it was just...
Dialogue: 0,1:04:29.28,1:04:31.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It was the emergence of the miraculous.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:31.28,1:04:34.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It was the emergence of the miraculous.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:34.28,1:04:36.28,Default,,0,0,0,,He should have hit me, you know.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:36.28,1:04:38.46,Default,,0,0,0,,He had no way to get off.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:38.46,1:04:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,,And this way, you turn your car over.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:40.46,1:04:44.42,Default,,0,0,0,,So how he managed to get half off and half on
Dialogue: 0,1:04:44.42,1:04:46.42,Default,,0,0,0,,and not turn his car over.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:46.42,1:04:51.21,Default,,0,0,0,,So if you look back over your life, then,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:51.21,1:04:55.38,Default,,0,0,0,,and recall many of the close calls in my life,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:55.38,1:04:58.38,Default,,0,0,0,,a lot of close calls.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:58.38,1:05:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,,A lot of close calls.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:00.38,1:05:03.48,Default,,0,0,0,,A piece of shrapnel missed my jugular vein by...
Dialogue: 0,1:05:03.48,1:05:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It just ticked the skin.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:05.76,1:05:06.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Boom!
Dialogue: 0,1:05:06.76,1:05:09.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Stuck in the bulkhead.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:09.11,1:05:12.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Exploding mine.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:12.13,1:05:16.67,Default,,0,0,0,,And, funny, this jugular vein must have some karma.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:16.67,1:05:18.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll have to ask him about it.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:22.63,1:05:25.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You say sick.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:25.05,1:05:28.05,Default,,0,0,0,,This jugular vein does have a karma to it.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:28.05,1:05:29.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:29.05,1:05:31.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess I can guess what it is.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:31.05,1:05:32.05,Default,,0,0,0,,What I'm guessing is correct.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:32.05,1:05:33.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:33.05,1:05:34.05,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:34.05,1:05:35.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:35.05,1:05:39.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Then one time I was on a ward with very psychotic patients.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:39.53,1:05:41.53,Default,,0,0,0,,And some guy, it wasn't my patient,
Dialogue: 0,1:05:41.53,1:05:43.53,Default,,0,0,0,,just came out of nowhere.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:43.53,1:05:47.65,Default,,0,0,0,,And what he'd done is broken a spoon,
Dialogue: 0,1:05:47.65,1:05:49.65,Default,,0,0,0,,scraped it on the cement,
Dialogue: 0,1:05:49.65,1:05:51.65,Default,,0,0,0,,made it into a very sharp shiv, you know.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:51.65,1:05:54.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, he was over here, my patient.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:54.76,1:05:55.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm here talking to him.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:55.76,1:05:56.76,Default,,0,0,0,,And I turn this way,
Dialogue: 0,1:05:56.76,1:05:58.76,Default,,0,0,0,,and the guy swings at me with his shiv.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:58.76,1:06:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,And just ticked right above the jugular vein.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:03.76,1:06:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Repeated episodes over your jugular vein.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:07.88,1:06:12.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, boys.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:12.46,1:06:15.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Best to go to church and say your prayers at night.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:15.46,1:06:19.30,Default,,0,0,0,,But this is how you pick up karmic patterns.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:19.30,1:06:20.30,Default,,0,0,0,,This is how, you know,
Dialogue: 0,1:06:20.30,1:06:23.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just showing you how you pick up a karmic pattern.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:23.30,1:06:24.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You begin to sense,
Dialogue: 0,1:06:24.30,1:06:29.30,Default,,0,0,0,,is this just accident that something is always just nearly missing your jugular vein?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:29.30,1:06:34.30,Default,,0,0,0,,And then you pick up that in some lifetime,
Dialogue: 0,1:06:34.30,1:06:38.46,Default,,0,0,0,,what I'm holding in mind was a fact.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:38.46,1:06:39.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:39.46,1:06:41.46,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact, I almost remember it.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:41.46,1:06:42.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:42.46,1:06:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it served him right anyway.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:56.36,1:06:59.65,Default,,0,0,0,,So I just thought I'd give you some commonplace,
Dialogue: 0,1:06:59.65,1:07:01.71,Default,,0,0,0,,commonplace examples.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:01.71,1:07:02.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Commonplace examples.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:02.71,1:07:05.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I've also told you how I did,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:05.71,1:07:06.71,Default,,0,0,0,,you know,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:06.71,1:07:08.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I've had surgery without anesthesia
Dialogue: 0,1:07:08.71,1:07:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,and was lifted into miraculous realms,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:11.80,1:07:13.80,Default,,0,0,0,,which brings up angels.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:13.80,1:07:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,We've never talked about angels.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:15.80,1:07:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:16.80,1:07:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Because the subject is so abused,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:18.80,1:07:22.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I hate to even bring up the subject.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:22.19,1:07:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,During this surgery,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:24.96,1:07:29.96,Default,,0,0,0,,that which lifted me out of the body was the angelic.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:29.96,1:07:31.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:31.30,1:07:33.82,Default,,0,0,0,,So when I went through surgery,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:33.82,1:07:34.82,Default,,0,0,0,,for instance,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:34.82,1:07:35.82,Default,,0,0,0,,without anesthesia,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:35.82,1:07:38.82,Default,,0,0,0,,and I just kept surrendering every instant to God,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:38.82,1:07:41.82,Default,,0,0,0,,let go resisting the pain,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:41.82,1:07:43.82,Default,,0,0,0,,which was frankly excruciating,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:43.82,1:07:46.92,Default,,0,0,0,,and just kept letting go, resisting it.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:46.92,1:07:48.55,Default,,0,0,0,,And all of a sudden,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:48.55,1:07:51.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I was like lifted up by an infinite softness.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:51.55,1:07:54.55,Default,,0,0,0,,And I knew it was angels.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:54.55,1:07:56.55,Default,,0,0,0,,One has,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:56.55,1:08:00.55,Default,,0,0,0,,it does have guardian angels.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:00.55,1:08:02.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I wasn't going to talk about that today.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:02.55,1:08:05.32,Default,,0,0,0,,We have permission to do this one.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:05.32,1:08:08.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone does have a guardian angel.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:08.63,1:08:12.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:12.59,1:08:16.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I always thought they were ladies' fantasies.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:16.48,1:08:18.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Ladies like angels.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:18.48,1:08:21.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Guys don't talk about angels much.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:21.48,1:08:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It ain't really a guy thing, you know what I mean?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:27.00,1:08:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Valhalla's made up of warriors,
Dialogue: 0,1:08:29.00,1:08:31.27,Default,,0,0,0,,you know what I mean?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:31.27,1:08:32.27,Default,,0,0,0,,On the other side,
Dialogue: 0,1:08:32.27,1:08:34.27,Default,,0,0,0,,there's a warrior spirit,
Dialogue: 0,1:08:34.27,1:08:35.27,Default,,0,0,0,,you know,
Dialogue: 0,1:08:35.27,1:08:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,with a Viking hat on and,
Dialogue: 0,1:08:37.40,1:08:40.23,Default,,0,0,0,,oh, oh, oh, oh,
Dialogue: 0,1:08:40.23,1:08:43.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Wagnerian proportions.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:43.52,1:08:47.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Women have very nice little angels
Dialogue: 0,1:08:47.13,1:08:57.89,Default,,0,0,0,,who whisper pleasant, wonderful things to them.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:57.89,1:09:01.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Could be true.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:01.11,1:09:05.39,Default,,0,0,0,,No, the angelic forces were infinitely,
Dialogue: 0,1:09:05.39,1:09:06.39,Default,,0,0,0,,they're always the same,
Dialogue: 0,1:09:06.39,1:09:08.39,Default,,0,0,0,,infinitely powerful
Dialogue: 0,1:09:08.39,1:09:12.93,Default,,0,0,0,,and simultaneously infinitely gentle.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:12.93,1:09:16.89,Default,,0,0,0,,And when I first experienced their presence
Dialogue: 0,1:09:16.89,1:09:18.89,Default,,0,0,0,,in a snowbank as a boy,
Dialogue: 0,1:09:18.89,1:09:19.89,Default,,0,0,0,,as a boy,
Dialogue: 0,1:09:19.89,1:09:22.35,Default,,0,0,0,,the field,
Dialogue: 0,1:09:22.35,1:09:26.35,Default,,0,0,0,,the field that replaced that which had been my personal self
Dialogue: 0,1:09:26.35,1:09:29.35,Default,,0,0,0,,had the same infinite power
Dialogue: 0,1:09:29.35,1:09:32.38,Default,,0,0,0,,and infinite softness
Dialogue: 0,1:09:32.38,1:09:34.38,Default,,0,0,0,,and gentleness.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:34.38,1:09:38.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Divinity and the great angels
Dialogue: 0,1:09:38.72,1:09:41.97,Default,,0,0,0,,are infinitely powerful.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:41.97,1:09:44.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't want to mess with them.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:44.72,1:09:45.72,Default,,0,0,0,,At the same time,
Dialogue: 0,1:09:45.72,1:09:47.72,Default,,0,0,0,,like a powder puff,
Dialogue: 0,1:09:47.72,1:09:50.44,Default,,0,0,0,,exquisitely soft
Dialogue: 0,1:09:50.44,1:09:52.44,Default,,0,0,0,,and infinitely powerful.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:52.44,1:09:54.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Not to be denied.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:54.44,1:09:56.47,Default,,0,0,0,,And yet,
Dialogue: 0,1:09:56.47,1:09:58.47,Default,,0,0,0,,you melt in the softness
Dialogue: 0,1:09:58.47,1:10:00.47,Default,,0,0,0,,of the presence,
Dialogue: 0,1:10:00.47,1:10:01.47,Default,,0,0,0,,which is
Dialogue: 0,1:10:01.47,1:10:03.64,Default,,0,0,0,,the presence of pure love.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:03.64,1:10:06.34,Default,,0,0,0,,And by that sign,
Dialogue: 0,1:10:06.34,1:10:07.34,Default,,0,0,0,,you know,
Dialogue: 0,1:10:07.34,1:10:10.81,Default,,0,0,0,,when you've reached a good place
Dialogue: 0,1:10:10.81,1:10:12.81,Default,,0,0,0,,through spiritual work,
Dialogue: 0,1:10:12.81,1:10:15.81,Default,,0,0,0,,that you're not in the void of nothingness
Dialogue: 0,1:10:15.81,1:10:18.81,Default,,0,0,0,,because the presence of God is exquisite
Dialogue: 0,1:10:18.81,1:10:21.85,Default,,0,0,0,,and makes it hard to function and walk
Dialogue: 0,1:10:21.85,1:10:24.56,Default,,0,0,0,,until you get used to it.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:25.56,1:10:26.56,Default,,0,0,0,,So,
Dialogue: 0,1:10:26.56,1:10:27.56,Default,,0,0,0,,is that enough on that?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:27.56,1:10:31.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh,
Dialogue: 0,1:10:31.07,1:10:32.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I have five more minutes.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:32.07,1:10:33.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:33.07,1:10:34.07,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:34.07,1:10:35.07,Default,,0,0,0,,So,
Dialogue: 0,1:10:35.07,1:10:36.07,Default,,0,0,0,,then there's periods of time.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:36.07,1:10:37.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You see,
Dialogue: 0,1:10:37.07,1:10:38.07,Default,,0,0,0,,spiritual evolution is bumpy and jumpy.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:38.07,1:10:40.07,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just not linear and nice.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:40.07,1:10:42.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You go through horrible periods,
Dialogue: 0,1:10:42.65,1:10:44.65,Default,,0,0,0,,12 years of agony and misery and suffering,
Dialogue: 0,1:10:44.65,1:10:45.65,Default,,0,0,0,,and suddenly,
Dialogue: 0,1:10:45.65,1:10:47.65,Default,,0,0,0,,the good fairy smiles at you
Dialogue: 0,1:10:47.65,1:10:48.65,Default,,0,0,0,,and your life is just transformed.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:48.65,1:10:49.65,Default,,0,0,0,,And you think,
Dialogue: 0,1:10:49.65,1:10:50.65,Default,,0,0,0,,what did I do?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:52.68,1:10:55.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like all the karmic patterns are undone.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:55.68,1:10:57.68,Default,,0,0,0,,And when you get above your negative karma,
Dialogue: 0,1:10:57.68,1:10:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,,you go into a good space.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:59.68,1:11:01.68,Default,,0,0,0,,And the greatest space,
Dialogue: 0,1:11:01.68,1:11:04.03,Default,,0,0,0,,the greatest space is
Dialogue: 0,1:11:04.03,1:11:06.03,Default,,0,0,0,,in my lifetime,
Dialogue: 0,1:11:06.03,1:11:07.03,Default,,0,0,0,,although during the war,
Dialogue: 0,1:11:07.03,1:11:08.03,Default,,0,0,0,,there was,
Dialogue: 0,1:11:08.03,1:11:09.03,Default,,0,0,0,,you know,
Dialogue: 0,1:11:09.03,1:11:10.03,Default,,0,0,0,,like this,
Dialogue: 0,1:11:10.03,1:11:11.03,Default,,0,0,0,,like a thing not going off
Dialogue: 0,1:11:11.03,1:11:12.03,Default,,0,0,0,,or next to you and blowing you off.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:12.03,1:11:13.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Was that miraculous?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:13.03,1:11:15.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see if that was miraculous.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:15.03,1:11:16.17,Default,,0,0,0,,That,
Dialogue: 0,1:11:16.17,1:11:17.17,Default,,0,0,0,,that mind
Dialogue: 0,1:11:17.17,1:11:18.17,Default,,0,0,0,,didn't go off
Dialogue: 0,1:11:18.17,1:11:20.17,Default,,0,0,0,,because of the miraculous resist.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:20.17,1:11:21.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:22.17,1:11:23.17,Default,,0,0,0,,So,
Dialogue: 0,1:11:23.17,1:11:24.17,Default,,0,0,0,,anyway,
Dialogue: 0,1:11:24.17,1:11:25.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't be telling you about it.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:25.17,1:11:26.17,Default,,0,0,0,,So,
Dialogue: 0,1:11:26.17,1:11:29.17,Default,,0,0,0,,that was what I told you about it.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:29.17,1:11:30.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It was,
Dialogue: 0,1:11:30.17,1:11:31.17,Default,,0,0,0,,it almost went off.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:31.17,1:11:32.17,Default,,0,0,0,,And this kid looks at me,
Dialogue: 0,1:11:32.17,1:11:33.17,Default,,0,0,0,,he,
Dialogue: 0,1:11:33.17,1:11:34.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I was a kid,
Dialogue: 0,1:11:34.17,1:11:35.17,Default,,0,0,0,,he was a kid,
Dialogue: 0,1:11:35.17,1:11:36.17,Default,,0,0,0,,both 17 or 18,
Dialogue: 0,1:11:36.17,1:11:37.17,Default,,0,0,0,,whatever.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:37.17,1:11:38.17,Default,,0,0,0,,And he said,
Dialogue: 0,1:11:38.17,1:11:39.17,Default,,0,0,0,,well,
Dialogue: 0,1:11:39.17,1:11:40.17,Default,,0,0,0,,what if it blows up?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:40.17,1:11:41.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I said,
Dialogue: 0,1:11:41.17,1:11:42.17,Default,,0,0,0,,so,
Dialogue: 0,1:11:42.17,1:11:43.75,Default,,0,0,0,,oh,
Dialogue: 0,1:11:43.75,1:11:44.75,Default,,0,0,0,,then we die.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:44.75,1:11:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,,So,
Dialogue: 0,1:11:45.84,1:11:46.84,Default,,0,0,0,,he said,
Dialogue: 0,1:11:46.84,1:11:47.84,Default,,0,0,0,,oh.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:47.84,1:11:48.84,Default,,0,0,0,,So,
Dialogue: 0,1:11:48.84,1:11:49.84,Default,,0,0,0,,the energy field was such,
Dialogue: 0,1:11:49.84,1:11:50.84,Default,,0,0,0,,it actually put him in a state of peace.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:50.84,1:11:52.03,Default,,0,0,0,,So,
Dialogue: 0,1:11:52.03,1:11:53.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I said,
Dialogue: 0,1:11:53.03,1:11:54.03,Default,,0,0,0,,if you blow up,
Dialogue: 0,1:11:54.03,1:11:55.03,Default,,0,0,0,,so we die.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:55.03,1:11:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,So,
Dialogue: 0,1:11:56.03,1:11:59.03,Default,,0,0,0,,you're in terror replaced by neutral.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:59.03,1:12:01.03,Default,,0,0,0,,When does this surrender to God,
Dialogue: 0,1:12:01.03,1:12:02.03,Default,,0,0,0,,huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:04.02,1:12:07.03,Default,,0,0,0,,So,
Dialogue: 0,1:12:07.03,1:12:09.03,Default,,0,0,0,,the miraculous occurs throughout our life,
Dialogue: 0,1:12:09.03,1:12:10.03,Default,,0,0,0,,apparently,
Dialogue: 0,1:12:10.03,1:12:12.03,Default,,0,0,0,,starting from consciousness level 200
Dialogue: 0,1:12:12.03,1:12:15.14,Default,,0,0,0,,and then becoming quite powerful
Dialogue: 0,1:12:15.14,1:12:18.14,Default,,0,0,0,,and very obvious in the 500s.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:18.14,1:12:20.14,Default,,0,0,0,,The so-called cities,
Dialogue: 0,1:12:20.14,1:12:23.14,Default,,0,0,0,,which are the famous field of the miraculous,
Dialogue: 0,1:12:23.14,1:12:25.14,Default,,0,0,0,,calibrates around 570.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:25.14,1:12:27.14,Default,,0,0,0,,And from 570,
Dialogue: 0,1:12:27.14,1:12:29.14,Default,,0,0,0,,calibration level 570 up to 70,
Dialogue: 0,1:12:29.14,1:12:30.14,Default,,0,0,0,,to 600,
Dialogue: 0,1:12:30.14,1:12:35.56,Default,,0,0,0,,the miraculous become first sporadic,
Dialogue: 0,1:12:35.56,1:12:38.56,Default,,0,0,0,,then they become more and more continuous
Dialogue: 0,1:12:38.56,1:12:40.56,Default,,0,0,0,,and finally quite profound,
Dialogue: 0,1:12:40.56,1:12:43.61,Default,,0,0,0,,finally almost continuous.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:43.61,1:12:46.52,Default,,0,0,0,,But I thought we should take a break
Dialogue: 0,1:12:46.52,1:12:49.60,Default,,0,0,0,,and we'll get into that later.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:49.60,1:12:50.60,Default,,0,0,0,,People who,
Dialogue: 0,1:12:50.60,1:12:52.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I've consciously experienced a miracle.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:52.60,1:12:56.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Good for you.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:56.65,1:12:59.48,Default,,0,0,0,,People who are lying.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:00.48,1:13:04.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Liars,
Dialogue: 0,1:13:04.14,1:13:05.14,Default,,0,0,0,,how many liars?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:06.14,1:13:09.14,Default,,0,0,0,,But not the miraculous.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:09.14,1:13:10.14,Default,,0,0,0,,He wouldn't be here to say
Dialogue: 0,1:13:10.14,1:13:12.14,Default,,0,0,0,,you've never experienced the miraculous.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:12.14,1:13:15.14,Default,,0,0,0,,We already calibrated that before the class.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:15.14,1:13:16.14,Default,,0,0,0,,All right,
Dialogue: 0,1:13:16.14,1:13:17.14,Default,,0,0,0,,so realizing that they are common,
Dialogue: 0,1:13:17.14,1:13:18.14,Default,,0,0,0,,familiar,
Dialogue: 0,1:13:18.14,1:13:19.14,Default,,0,0,0,,that they're normal,
Dialogue: 0,1:13:19.14,1:13:20.14,Default,,0,0,0,,that they're part of evolution,
Dialogue: 0,1:13:20.14,1:13:21.14,Default,,0,0,0,,that they're part of the evolution
Dialogue: 0,1:13:21.14,1:13:23.14,Default,,0,0,0,,of your consciousness,
Dialogue: 0,1:13:23.14,1:13:25.14,Default,,0,0,0,,that they're automatic consequence
Dialogue: 0,1:13:25.14,1:13:27.14,Default,,0,0,0,,to your own spiritual development,
Dialogue: 0,1:13:27.14,1:13:29.14,Default,,0,0,0,,increases your awareness of the phenomenon.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:29.14,1:13:32.14,Default,,0,0,0,,And as your awareness increases,
Dialogue: 0,1:13:32.14,1:13:35.14,Default,,0,0,0,,the frequency naturally seems to increase.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:35.14,1:13:38.14,Default,,0,0,0,,It's only just that you're noticing them now all the time.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:38.14,1:13:39.14,Default,,0,0,0,,All right,
Dialogue: 0,1:13:39.14,1:13:41.23,Default,,0,0,0,,so we will take a break for how long?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:41.23,1:13:42.23,Default,,0,0,0,,15 minutes,
Dialogue: 0,1:13:42.23,1:13:46.10,Default,,0,0,0,,14 and a half minutes.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:46.10,1:13:47.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
